%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22German%20Envoy%3A%20Negotiations%20Over%20G20%20Declaration%20Showed%20That%20It%20Was%20%E2%80%9818%20Versus%202%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F30232303%2FFbGLloPUEAE3D1V.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20German%20ambassador%20to%20India%2C%20Philipp%20Ackermann%2C%20stressed%20that%20negotiations%20over%20the%20language%20related%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20in%20the%20G20%20declaration%20showed%20that%20the%20emerging%20countries%20were%20on%20the%20West%E2%80%99s%20side%20against%20the%20duo%20of%20Russia%20and%20China%2C%20which%20had%20to%20be%20consolidated%20with%20the%20final%20document%2C%20ensuring%20that%20group%20did%20not%20fail%20during%20India%E2%80%99s%20presidency.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Saturday%20afternoon%2C%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20announced%20that%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fg20-modi-new-delhi-declaration-consensus%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econsensus%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20been%20reached%20on%20the%20final%20declaration%20of%20the%20group%20of%2020%20major%20economies.%20It%20was%20a%20surprise%20move%20a%20day%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20summit%2C%20since%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20language%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98Bali%20paragraph%E2%80%99%20on%20Ukraine%20had%20been%20unacceptable%20to%20Russia%20and%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20on%20Friday%20night%2C%20India%2C%20along%20with%20Brazil%2C%20South%20Africa%20and%20Indonesia%20%E2%80%93%20all%20developing%20countries%20that%20are%20holding%20G20%20presidencies%20in%20consecutive%20years%20%E2%80%93%20pitched%20a%20new%20draft%20text%20on%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20it%20presented%20as%20the%20last%20ultimatum%20with%20the%20only%20alternate%20being%20to%20talk%20to%20Modi.%20That%20strategy%20worked%20and%20the%2018%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20G20%20summit%20avoided%20the%20prospect%20of%20not%20having%20a%20joint%20statement%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Western%20leadership%20declared%20%E2%80%9Csuccess%E2%80%9D%2C%20there%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fglobal-media-highlights-watered-down-statement-on-russia-ukraine-after-modis-g20-pr-push%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econsiderable%20criticism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20G20%20declaration%20had%20seen%20a%20climbdown%20for%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20language%20of%20the%20Bali%20declaration%20that%20condemned%20Russia%20for%20the%20war%20against%20Ukraine%20was%20gone.%20Instead%2C%20all%2020%20members%20endorsed%20the%20respect%20for%20states%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%9Cterritorial%20integrity%20and%20sovereignty%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUkraine%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20ministry%20claimed%20that%20the%20declaration%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnothing%20to%20be%20proud%20of%E2%80%9D%2C%20while%20Russia%20claimed%20it%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvictory%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwhy-china-and-russia-are-the-biggest-winners-of-indias-g20-presidency%5C%22%3EWhy%20China%20and%20Russia%20Are%20the%20Biggest%20Winners%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20G20%20Presidency%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Ackermann%20said%20that%20Germany%20was%20of%20the%20view%20that%20G20%20was%20one%20of%20the%20last%20forums%20where%20everybody%20was%20around%20the%20table.%20He%20stated%20that%20if%20the%20summit%20had%20ended%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20a%20consensus%20declaration%2C%20%5Bthat%5D%20would%20have%20been%20a%20kind%20of%20death%20to%20the%20G20%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%20officials%20directly%20involved%20in%20the%20negotiations%20had%20conveyed%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdynamic%20very%20early%20was%2018%20versus%20two%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20the%20emerging%20markets%20aligned%20on%20issues%20against%20Russia%20and%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAckermann%20said%20the%20German%20chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20left%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20satisfied%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20summit%2C%20as%20it%20fulfilled%20his%20two%20aims%20%E2%80%93%20to%20make%20a%20success%20of%20the%20Indian%20presidency%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20Ukraine%20war%20should%20find%20an%20appropriate%20place%20in%20the%20Delhi%20declaration%20in%20line%20with%20the%20one%20achieved%20last%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20German%20envoy%20claimed%20that%20the%20outcome%20%E2%80%9Cexceeded%E2%80%9D%20expectations.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20declaration%20went%20further%E2%80%9D%20than%20Bali%2C%20as%20it%20%E2%80%9Creflected%E2%80%9D%20the%20developments%20over%20the%20last%20one%20year%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAckermann%20noted%20that%20from%20their%20perspective%2C%20the%20declaration%20had%20strong%20language%20against%20the%20use%20of%20force%20for%20territorial%20acquisition%20and%20that%20the%20use%20of%20nuclear%20threats%20was%20unacceptable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20the%20Russian%20foreign%20minister%20Sergei%20Lavrov%20had%20highlighted%20that%20there%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20Russia%2C%20except%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20Black%20Sea%20grain%20deal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fg20-new-india-plays-an-old-game-walking-in-the-footsteps-of-nehru%5C%22%3EG20%3A%20Modi%20Plays%20an%20Old%20Game%2C%20Walking%20in%20the%20Footsteps%20of%20Nehru%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20some%20things%20that%20Lavrov%20said%20and%20I%20think%20they%20are%20all%20not%20very%20convincing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ackerman%20noted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20agree%20that%20Russia%20has%20not%20been%20mentioned%20%E2%80%93%20but%20it%20has%20Russia%20written%20all%20over%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmaximal%E2%80%9D%20stance%20on%20language%20%E2%80%9Cwould%20not%20have%20led%20to%20success%E2%80%9D%2C%20describing%20the%20declaration%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfabulous%20text%E2%80%9D%20for%20such%20a%20%E2%80%9Cheterogenous%20group%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERussia%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20global%20south%20had%20stopped%20the%20West%20from%20%E2%80%9CUkrainising%E2%80%9D%20the%20G20%20agenda.%20On%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20geo-political%20divide%2C%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20said%20that%20the%20G20%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20the%20forum%20for%20political%20discussions%E2%80%9D%20to%20play%20down%20the%20watering-down%20of%20the%20text%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694573571000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F30232303%2FFbGLloPUEAE3D1V.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnegotiations-over-g20-declaration-showed-it-was-18-v-2-ackermann-says%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Philipp%20Ackermann%20also%20said%20that%20if%20the%20summit%20had%20ended%20without%20a%20consensus%20declaration%2C%20it%20%E2%80%9Cwould%20have%20been%20a%20kind%20of%20death%20to%20the%20G20%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnegotiations-over-g20-declaration-showed-it-was-18-v-2-ackermann-says%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20Hijab%20Cases%2C%20One%20Lesson%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2