a%20as%20even%20more%20'convincing'%20than%20against%20Pakistan.%20India%20had%20beaten%20Pakistan%20by%20228%20runs%20on%20Monday.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20victory%20for%20me%20was%20more%20convincing%20than%20Pakistan.%20We%20won%20against%20Pakistan%20by%20228%20runs%20but%20this%20would%20give%20them%20a%20lot%20of%20confidence%2C%26quot%3B%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20said%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20doubt%20about%20the%20batting%20unit.%20There%20were%20always%20doubts%20about%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20coming%20back%20after%20an%20injury.%20Then%20you%20got%20Kuldeep%20and%20the%20other%20bowlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20defending%20217%20on%20this%20wicket%2C%20plus%20the%20conditions.%20I%20know%20there%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20grip%20on%20the%20wicket%20but%20it%20gripped%20more%20in%20%C2%A0the%20first%20innings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGambhir%20added%20the%20gritty%20win%20against%20a%20team%20like%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20which%20plays%20spin%20really%20well%2C%20will%20give%20the%20team%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDefending%20217%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20they%20are%20a%20really%20good%20side%20playing%20against%20spin.%20This%20would%20give%20them%20a%20lot%20of%20confidence%20going%20into%20the%20final%20and%20then%20the%20World%20Cup.%20because%20the%20moment%20your%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20start%20firing%2C%20I%20think%20it%20gives%20a%20lot%20of%20confidence%20to%20the%20captain%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Indian%20bowlers%20produced%20a%20splendid%20collective%20effort%20to%20carry%20their%20team%20to%20a%2041-run%20win%20over%20a%20spirited%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%20a%20Super%204%20match%2C%20and%20into%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20final%20on%20Tuesday.%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20fifty%20(53%20off%2048%20balls)%20was%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20India's%20sub-par%20213%20after%20Lankan%20spinners%20Dunith%20Wellalage%20(5%2F40)%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Charith%20Asalanka%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F110487-charith-asalanka-playerprofile%5C%22%3ECharith%20Asalanka%3C%2Fa%3E%20(4%2F18)%20bamboozled%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20India%2C%20guided%20by%20Kuldeep%20Yadav's%204%20for%2043%2C%20bowled%20out%20Sri%20Lanka%20for%20172.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20who%20entered%20the%20final%20with%20four%20points%2C%20will%20either%20face%20Sri%20Lanka%20or%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20summit%20clash%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20hosts%20will%20face%20Pakistan%20in%20a%20crunch%20match%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20insipid%20effort%20of%20their%20batsmen%20made%20it%20mandatory%20for%20the%20Indian%20bowlers%20to%20be%20on%20the%20money%20from%20ball%20one%2C%20and%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20led%20the%20way%20with%20some%20great%20bowling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694571300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fi7p26248_india-celebrates_625x300_13_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fgautam-gambhir-terms-indias-win-over-sri-lanka-as-more-convincing-than-pakistan-victory-this-is-why-4384488%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20India%20vs%20Sri%20Lanka%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20Super%204%20clash%20went%20down%20to%20the%20wire%20though%20the%20scoreboard%20might%20not%20suggest%20so.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fgautam-gambhir-terms-indias-win-over-sri-lanka-as-more-convincing-than-pakistan-victory-this-is-why-4384488%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fgautam-gambhir-terms-indias-win-over