itting%20the%20company's%20biggest%20source%20of%20revenue.%20Troubles%20in%20China%2C%20where%20it%20faces%20a%20widening%20government%20ban%20and%20competition%20with%20an%20advanced%20new%20phone%20from%20Huawei%20Technologies%20Co.%2C%20have%20only%20added%20to%20the%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20Apple%20will%20keep%20the%20lower-end%20version%20of%20the%20iPhone%2015%20at%20%24799%2C%20while%20the%20entry-level%20Pro%20model%20remains%20at%20%24999%20-%20a%20price%20that%20was%20considered%20eye-popping%20when%20the%20iPhone%20X%20debuted%20at%20that%20level%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20starting%20Pro%20Max%20will%20be%20nearly%2010%25%20more%20expensive%20than%20the%20cheapest%20iPhone%2014%20Pro%20Max%2C%20it%20has%20256%20gigabytes%20of%20storage%2C%20compared%20with%20the%20128%20gigabytes%20offered%20previously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnderscoring%20the%20incremental%20nature%20of%20this%20price%20increase%2C%20Apple%20didn't%20raise%20the%20levels%20of%20its%20iPhone%2015%20Pro%20Max%20models%20with%20higher%20amounts%20of%20storage.%20The%20version%20with%20512%20gigabytes%20remains%20at%20%241%2C399%2C%20while%20one%20with%201%20terabyte%20still%20costs%20%241%2C599.%20But%20even%20with%20prices%20staying%20the%20same%2C%20Apple%20is%20able%20to%20earn%20higher%20margins%20because%20the%20cost%20of%20storage%20has%20fallen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20is%20boosting%20prices%20more%20aggressively%20outside%20the%20US.%20The%20iPhone%2015%20Pro%20will%20rise%20by%20%2450%20in%20Canada%2C%20with%20the%20Pro%20Max%20price%20going%20up%20%24200.%20In%20India%2C%20the%20Pro%20Max%20will%20climb%20by%20about%2014%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20countries%2C%20however%2C%20are%20getting%20a%20price%20decrease.%20In%20the%20UK%2C%20the%20iPhone%2015%20Pro%20and%20Pro%20Max%20are%20100%20pounds%20(%24125)%20cheaper%20than%20their%20predecessors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20iPhone%20pricing%20tweaks%2C%20Apple%20is%20generating%20more%20revenue%20from%20ad