un-violence-new-mexico%5C%22%3Esolutions%20to%20gun%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Bprotect%20the%20Second%20Amendment%20rights%20of%20law-abiding%20citizens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20find%20all%20the%20legal%20pathways%20that%20we%20possibly%20can%20to%20curb%20gun%20violence%20in%20our%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20Vasquez%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20I%20will%20support%20the%20pathways%20that%20are%20constitutional.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELujan%20Grisham's%20order%C2%A0forbids%20anyone%20besides%20a%20police%20officer%20or%20licensed%20security%20officer%20from%20carrying%20a%20firearm%20in%20public%20in%20%26quot%3Bcities%20or%20counties%20averaging%201%2C000%20or%20more%20violent%20crimes%20per%20100%2C000%20resident%20per%20year%20since%202021.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20practice%2C%20the%20order%20applies%20only%20to%20Albuquerque%20%E2%80%94%20the%20state's%20largest%20city%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20county%20surrounding%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22From%20left%3A%20New%20Mexico%20Reps.%20Melanie%20Stansbury%2C%20Gabe%20Vasquez%2C%20and%20Teresa%20Ledger%20Fernandez.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65010a79992da60019eb245d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrom%20left%3A%20New%20Mexico%20Reps.%20Melanie%20Stansbury%2C%20Gabe%20Vasquez%2C%20and%20Teresa%20Leger%20Fernandez.%3Cp%3ECaroline%20Brehman%20and%20Bill%20Clark%2FCQ-Roll%20Call%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELujan%20Grisham%20issued%20the%20order%20after%20an%2011-year-old%20boy%2C%20Froylan%20Villegas%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kob.com%2Fnew-mexico%2Fwere-just-against-shootings-in-general-family-of-froylan-villegas-hopes-for-arrest-soon%2F%5C%22%3Ewas%20fatally%20shot%20on%20Wednesday%20night%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20a%20baseball%20game%20in%20Albuquerque.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp