ontent%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPraising%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20policies%20in%20the%20Russian%20port%20town%20of%20Vladivostok%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20said%20that%20PM%20Modi%20is%20just%20doing%20the%20%26quot%3Bright%20thing%26quot%3B%20in%20promoting%20the%20Make%20in%20India%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20the%20remarks%20while%20speaking%20at%20the%208th%20Eastern%20Economic%20Forum%20(EEF)%20in%20response%20to%20a%20media%20query%20on%20Russian-made%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutin%20said%20that%20domestically%20made%20automobiles%20must%20be%20used%20and%20India%20has%20already%20set%20examples%20through%20its%20policies%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20address%20at%20the%20forum%2C%20Putin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20we%20did%20not%20have%20domestically%20made%20cars%20then%2C%20but%20we%20do%20now.%20It%20is%20true%20that%20they%20look%20more%20modest%20than%20Mercedes%20or%20Audi%20cars%2C%20which%20we%20bought%20in%20vast%20amounts%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20but%20this%20is%20not%20an%20issue.%20I%20think%20that%20we%20should%20emulate%20many%20of%20our%20partners%2C%20for%20example%2C%20India.%20They%20are%20focused%20on%20the%20manufacture%20and%20use%20of%20Indian-made%20vehicles.%20I%20think%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20is%20doing%20the%20right%20thing%20in%20promoting%20the%20Make%20in%20India%20programme.%20He%20is%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20is%20absolutely%20fine%20to%20use%20Russian-made%20automobiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20%5BRussian-made%5D%20automobiles%2C%20and%20we%20must%20use%20them%3B%20this%20is%20absolutely%20fine.%20This%20will%20not%20lead%20to%20any%20infringements%20of%20our%20WTO%20obligations%2C%20absolutely%20not.%20It%20will%20concern%20state%20purchases.%20We%20must%20create%20a%20certain%20chain%20regarding%20what%20cars%20different%20classes%20of%20officials%20can%20drive%2C%20so%20that%20they%20will%20use%20domestically-made%20cars%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said%20in%20Vladivostok%2C%20according%20to%20a%20transcript%20of%20the%20plenary%20session%20posted%20on%20Kremlin's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20probably%20know%20about%20the%20proposals%20to%20continue%20buying%20these%20cars.%20It%20would%20be%20easy%20to%20do%2C%20because%20the%20logistics%20are%20streamlined%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20this%2C%20but%20the%20Russian%20President%20also%20talked%20at%20length%20how%20he%20sees%20nothing%20in%20the%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Economic%20Corridor%20(IMEC)%20that%20can%20hinder%20Russia%20and%20that%20the%20project%20according%20to%20him%20benefits%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20jumped%20into%20the%20%26quot%3Blast%20car%26quot%3B%20by%20agreeing%20with%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20India%20on%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20new%20economic%20corridor%20but%20the%20project%20itself%20is%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20Russia%2C%20Putin%20said%20while%20speaking%20at%20the%20Eastern%20Economic%20Forum%20(EEF)%20as%20cited%20by%20the%20Russian%20news%20agency%20TASS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20President%20said%20that%20the%20IMEC%20would%20help%20his%20country%20develop%20logistics%20and%20added%20that%20the%20project%20had%20been%20under%20discussion%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20came%20after%20India%2C%20the%20US%2C%20UAE%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20France%2C%20Germany%2C%20Italy%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20on%20Saturday%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20signed%20a%20Memorandum%20of%20Understanding%20(MoU)%20to%20establish%20the%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Economic%20Corridor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20forum%2C%20Putin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20this%20will%20only%20benefit%20us.%20I%20believe%20that%20this%20will%20only%20help%20us%20develop%20logistics.%20Firstly%2C%20this%20project%20has%20been%20discussed%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20for%20several%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrue%2C%20the%20Americans%20jumped%20on%20this%20train%20at%20the%20last%20moment.%20But%20for%20them%2C%20I%20don't%20see%20much%20point%20in%20being%20in%20this%20project.%20Only%2C%20perhaps%2C%20from%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20business%20interest.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20additional%20movement%20of%20goods%20along%20this%20corridor%20is%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20an%20addition%20to%20our%20North-South%20project.%20We%20have%20nothing%20here%20we%20see%20something%20that%20could%20somehow%20hinder%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20on%20Saturday%20(September%209)%2C%20announced%20a%20historic%20agreement%20to%20soon%20launch%20a%20mega%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20shipping%20and%20railway%20connectivity%20corridor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20made%20the%20announcement%20for%20the%20ambitious%20project%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20which%20took%20place%20in%20New%20Delhi%20under%20India's%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20first-of-its-kind%20initiative%20on%20cooperation%20on%20connectivity%20and%20infrastructure%20involving%20India%2C%20UAE%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20EU%2C%20France%2C%20Italy%2C%20Germany%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20after%20the%20launch%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20cordially%20welcome%20you%20all%20at%20this%20event.%20I%20am%20very%20happy%20to%20co-chair%20this%20event%20with%20my%20friend%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%20Today%20we%20all%20have%20seen%20the%20conclusion%20of%20a%20historic%20and%20important%20agreement.%20In%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20it%20will%20be%20an%20effective%20medium%20of%20economic%20integration%20between%20India%2C%20South%20Asia%2C%20and%20Europe%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%