0%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Turkey%20TF%20KAAN%20stealth%20fighter%20jet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65009b1e7cfadd001913ba37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221139%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20TF%20KAAN%20at%20its%20presentation%20ceremony%20in%20Ankara%20on%20May%201.%3Cp%3EYavuz%20Ozden%2F%20dia%20images%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3ERelying%20on%20the%20GE%20F110%2C%20which%20is%20better%20known%20for%20its%20use%20in%20the%20F-16%20and%20other%20older%20US%20jets%2C%20will%20leave%20the%20TF%20Kaan%20at%20a%20disadvantage%20against%20future%20Greek%20F-35s.%20Bohl%20said%20the%20jet%20will%20most%20likely%20%26quot%3Bserve%20as%20a%20slow%20replacement%26quot%3B%20for%20Turkey's%20large%20F-16%20fleet%20rather%20than%20as%20a%20counterweight%20to%20Greece's%20F-35.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EThis%20suggests%20that%20even%20if%20Turkish%20Aerospace%20Industries%20meets%20its%20ambitious%20rollout%20date%2C%20the%20TF%20Kaan%20still%20won't%20deny%20Greece%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fpauliddon%2F2022%2F07%2F02%2Feven-if-turkey-gets-modernized-f-16s-greece-will-still-have-a-technological-edge-in-airpower%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20technological%20edge%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20Turkey's%20larger%20air%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EGeorge%20Tzogopoulos%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Centre%20International%20de%20Formation%20Europ%C3%A9enne%2C%20a%20French%20policy%20research%20institute%2C%20believes%20Greece's%20timeframe%20for%20receiving%20F-35s%20is%20more%20realistic%20than%20Turkey's%20for%20the%20TF%20Kaan%20since%20the%20latter%20%26quot%3Bdepends%20on%20several%20unknown%20parameters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Turkish%20defense%20industry%20has%20already%20made%20progress%20(e.g.%2C%2