e%20and%20methane%20detected%C2%A0in%20K2-18%20b's%20atmosphere.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20want%20to%20see%20those%20kinds%20of%20studies%20really%20digging%20into%3A%20'Is%20this%20a%20unique%20signature%20of%20a%20water%20ocean%20or%20not%3F'%20%E2%80%94%20because%20it's%20such%20an%20indirect%20argument%20%E2%80%94%20before%20I'd%20be%20really%20comfortable%20saying%20there's%20liquid%20water%20under%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Kempton%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20ocean%20does%20exist%2C%20Madhusudhan%20said%2C%20there's%20a%20chance%20it%20would%20be%20too%20hot%20for%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInsider%20science%20reporter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fmarianne-guenot-ins%5C%22%3EMarianne%20Guenot%3C%2Fa%3E%20contributed%20reporting%20to%20this%20story.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-planet-habitability-discoveries-nasa-james-webb-space-telescope-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694548254000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6500b9a07cfadd001913e480%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-planet-habitability-discoveries-nasa-james-webb-space-telescope-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NASA's%20James%20Webb%20Space%20Telescope%20revealed%20that%20exoplanet%20K2-18%20b%20may%20be%20an%20ocean%20world%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20chance%20it%20could%20harbor%20alien%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mmcfalljohnsen%40insider.com%20(Morgan%20McFall-Johnsen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A155%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-planet-habitability-discoveries-nasa-james-webb-space-telescope-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20just%20announced%20the%20Apple%20Watch%20Series%209%20%E2%80%94%20here's%20what's%20new%20and%20h