-to-pakistan-on-october-21-shehbaz-sharif%2Farticleshow%2F103616284.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103616284.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFormer%20Pakistani%20prime%20minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20has%20announced%20that%20his%20brother%2C%20Nawaz%20Sharif%2C%20will%20return%20to%20Pakistan%20on%20October%2021%20to%20lead%20the%20party's%20political%20campaign%20for%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20was%20disqualified%20from%20holding%20public%20office%20in%202017%20and%20has%20been%20in%20exile%20in%20London%20since%20then.%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20expressed%20optimism%20that%20the%20country%20and%20economy%20will%20progress%20once%20again%20under%20his%20brother's%20leadership.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Omer%20Farooq%20Khan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fnawaz-sharif-to-return-to-pakistan-on-october-21-shehbaz-sharif%2Farticleshow%2F103616284.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fnawaz-sharif-to-return-to-pakistan-on-october-21-shehbaz-sharif%2Famp_articleshow%2F103616284.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fnawaz-sharif-to-return-to-pakistan-on-october-21-shehbaz-sharif%2Famp_articleshow%2F103616284.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Seat-Sharing%20On%20Agenda%20At%20INDIA's%20First%20Coordination%20Panel%20Meet%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENegotiations%20on%20the%20seat-sharing%20formula%20and%20evolving%20a%20broad%20outlay%20of%20campaign%20strategy%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20will%20be%20high%20on%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20Opposition%20INDIA%20bloc's%20Coordination%20Committee%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20of%20the%2014-member%20all-important%20panel%20of%20the%20opposition%20will%20take%20place%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20NCP%20leader%20Sharad%20Pawar%20in%20Delhi%20tomorrow%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20leaders%20of%20several%20opposition%20parties%20have%20sought%20an%20early%20seat-sharing%20formula%20to%20be%20worked%20out%20to%20ensure%20that%20a%20joint%20candidate%20is%20put%20up%20from%20the%20opposition%20side%20against%20the%20BJP%20candidates%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20several%20leaders%20said%20that%20the%20parties%20have%20to%20%26quot%3Bshed%20their%20egos%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bvested%20interests%26quot%3B%20in%20arriving%20at%20such%20a%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20no%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20on%20the%20criteria%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20based%20on%20the%20performance%20of%20parties%20on%20a%20particular%20seat%20in%20recent%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20source%20aware%20of%20the%20details%20said%20the%20issue%20of%20seat%20sharing%20will%20be%20addressed%2C%20even%20if%20it%20may%20not%20be%20finalised%20in%20tomorrow's%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20leaders%20will%20also%20focus%20on%20a%20broad%20outlay%20of%20the%20election%20campaign%20for%20taking%20on%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20panel%20member%20Raghav%20Chadha%20said%20it%20will%20have%20discussions%20on%20issues%20like%20reaching%20out%20to%20people%2C%20planning%20joint%20rallies%2C%20and%20working%20out%20door-to-door%20campaigns%2C%20which%20will%20be%20different%20for%20each%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20political%20party%20will%20have%20to%20sacrifice%20three%20things%20to%20make%20this%20alliance%20successful%20-%20ambition%20(%3Cem%3Emahatvakanksha%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20a%20difference%20of%20opinion%20(%3Cem%3Ematbhed%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20%3Cem%3Emanbhed%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chadha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20coordination%20cum%20election%20strategy%20committee%20of%20the%20opposition's%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%2014%20members%20-%20K%20C%20Venugopal%20(Congress)%2C%20T%20R%20Baalu%20(DMK)%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%20(JMM)%2C%20Sanjay%20Raut%20(Shiv%20Sena-UBT)%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20(RJD)%2C%20Raghav%20Chadha%20(AAP)%2C%20Javed%20Ali%20Khan%20(SP)%2C%20Lalan%20Singh%20(JDU)%2C%20D%20Raja%20(CPI)%2C%20Omar%20Abdullah%20(National%20Conference)%2C%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20(PDP)%2C%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20(TMC)%2C%20and%20a%20member%20from%20the%20CPIM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20was%20summoned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20to%20appear%20before%20it%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20will%20not%20attend%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CPIM%20has%20not%20yet%20nominated%20any%20member%20to%20the%20committee%20and%20will%20be%20absent%20at%20the%20meeting%20as%20well.%20Party%20sources%20said%20a%20decision%20on%20who%20will%20represent%20CPIM%20will%20be%20taken%20at%20its%20politburo%20meeting%20scheduled%20on%20September%2016-17.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20in%20Patna%20in%20June%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20the%20strongest%20candidate%20from%20each%20seat%20would%20be%20picked%20up%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20issued%20on%20September%201%2C%20after%20the%20third%20meeting%20of%20the%20bloc%2C%20said%20the%20parties%20would%20contest%20polls%20together%20%26quot%3Bas%20far%20as%20possible%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20that%20seat%20sharing%20in%20arrangements%20in%20different%20states%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Binitiated%20immediately%26quot%3B%20and%20concluded%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20earliest%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20while%20states%20like%20Maharashtra%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Bihar%20are%20sorted%2C%20others%20like%20Delhi%2C%20Punjab%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20will%20also%20focus%20on%20finalising%20campaigns%20a