2originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-court-reserves-verdict-on-imran-khans-plea-against-cipher-case-trial-in-punjab-jail%2Farticleshow%2F103616211.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103616211.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Pakistani%20high%20court%20has%20reserved%20its%20verdict%20on%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20former%20prime%20minister%20Imran%20Khan%20challenging%20the%20decision%20to%20conduct%20his%20trial%20in%20the%20cipher%20case%20at%20Attock%20jail.%20Imran%20Khan%20was%20sent%20to%20jail%20following%20his%20conviction%20in%20the%20Toshakhana%20graft%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Omer%20Farooq%20Khan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-court-reserves-verdict-on-imran-khans-plea-against-cipher-case-trial-in-punjab-jail%2Farticleshow%2F103616211.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-court-reserves-verdict-on-imran-khans-plea-against-cipher-case-trial-in-punjab-jail%2Famp_articleshow%2F103616211.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-court-reserves-verdict-on-imran-khans-plea-against-cipher-case-trial-in-punjab-jail%2Famp_articleshow%2F103616211.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20Bows%20To%20EU%20And%20Unveils%20iPhone%20With%20USB-C%20Charger%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EApple%20unveiled%20its%20new%20iPhone%20lineup%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20with%20its%20Lightning%20charger%20ports%20replaced%20on%20the%20newest%20models%20by%20a%20universal%20charger%20after%20a%20tussle%20with%20the%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20bloc%20is%20insisting%20that%20all%20phones%20and%20other%20small%20devices%20must%20be%20compatible%20with%20the%20USB-C%20charging%20cables%20from%20the%20end%20of%20next%20year%2C%20a%20move%20it%20says%20will%20reduce%20waste%20and%20save%20money%20for%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20had%20long%20argued%20that%20its%20cable%20was%20more%20secure%20than%20USB-C%20chargers%2C%20which%20are%20already%20deployed%20by%20Apple%20on%20other%20devices%20and%20widely%20used%20by%20rivals%20including%20the%20world's%20biggest%20smartphone%20maker%20Samsung.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUSB-C%20has%20become%20a%20universally%20accepted%20standard.%20So%20we're%20bringing%20USB-C%20to%20iPhone%2015%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kaiann%20Drance%2C%20Apple's%20vice%20president%20of%20iPhone%20marketing%20at%20a%20launch%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20comes%20as%20Apple%20faces%20declining%20sales%20of%20iPhones%2C%20with%20higher%20prices%20pushing%20customers%20to%20delay%20switching%20to%20newer%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20is%20also%20caught%20up%20in%20diplomatic%20turbulence%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20China%2C%20with%20reports%20saying%20the%20communist%20government%20is%20banning%20civil%20servants%20from%20using%20its%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEasier%20repair%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20any%20other%20company%2C%20Apple%20would%20prefer%20to%20boast%20about%20shiny%20new%20features%20rather%20than%20new%20charging%20ports.%20However%2C%20analysts%20agree%20that%20the%20switch%20to%20USB-C%20was%20going%20to%20be%20the%20main%20headline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEU%20policymakers%20said%20the%20rule%20would%20simplify%20the%20lives%20of%20Europeans%20and%20do%20away%20with%20a%20mountain%20of%20obsolete%20chargers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cable%20change%20may%20give%20consumers%20pause%2C%20but%20within%20a%20generation%2C%20they%20will%20get%20over%20it%3A%20They%20won't%20have%20a%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Techsponential%20analyst%20Avi%20Greengart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20rolling%20improvements%20to%20iPhone%20cameras%20and%20chips%2C%20Apple%20also%20said%20that%20the%20iPhone%2015%2C%20which%20includes%20four%20varieties%2C%20would%20have%20internal%20components%20that%20simplify%20repair%20and%20a%20new%20frame%20that%20allows%20the%20back%20glass%20to%20be%20easily%20replaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20openness%20to%20repair%20is%20an%20unexpected%20turnaround.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20last%20month%20said%20it%20was%20endorsing%20the%20passage%20of%20a%20California%20law%20requiring%20major%20gadget%20makers%20to%20enable%20people%20to%20fix%20their%20devices%20without%20taking%20them%20back%20to%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20also%20unveiled%20new%20models%20of%20the%20Apple%20Watch%20that%20would%20respond%20to%20a%20tap%20of%20the%20index%20finger%20and%20thumb%20to%20start%20and%20stop%20calls%20or%20other%20key%20functions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESales%20of%20iPhones%20in%20the%20recently%20ended%20quarter%20lagged%20analyst%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20suffered%20a%202.4%20percent%20drop%20in%20iPhone%20sales%2C%20which%20account%20for%20nearly%20half%20of%20the%20total%20revenues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20shares%20were%20battered%20last%20week%20following%20reports%20of%20significant%20Chinese%20restrictions%20on%20iPhones%20at%20government%20offices%20and%20state-backed%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20is%20a%20very%20important%20market%20for%20Apple%2C%20so%20any%20negative%20sentiment%20by%20the%20Chinese%20government%20toward%20Apple%20is%20concerning%2C%26quot%3B%20analyst%20Greengart%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20reported%20%2415.8%20billion%20in%20revenues%20from%20China%20in%20the%20most%20recent%20quarter%2C%20nearly%2020%20percent%20of%20total%20revenues.%20Executives%20pointed%20to%20the%20uptick%20in%20China%20sales%20in%20a%20period%20when%20overall%20sales%20fell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWedbush%20analyst%20Dan%20Ives%20estimated%20that%20a%20Chinese%20government%20ban%20would%20affect%20less%20than%20500%2C000%20iPhones