ailable%20on%20last%20year's%20Pro%20models.%20This%20year%2C%20all%20of%20Apple's%20iPhone%20models%20are%20equipped%20with%20a%20USB%20Type-C%20port%2C%20making%20them%20the%20first%20handsets%20to%20arrive%20without%20Apple's%20proprietary%20Lightning%20charging%20port.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EiPhone%2015%2C%20iPhone%2015%20Plus%20pricing%20and%20availability%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EiPhone%2015%20pricing%20in%20India%20starts%20at%20Rs.%2079%2C900%20while%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gadgets360.com%2Fapple-iphone-15-plus-price-in-india-115760%5C%22%3EiPhone%2015%20Plus%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs.%2089%2C900%20for%20the%20base%20128GB%20variant.%20Both%20phones%20will%20be%20available%20in%20Black%2C%20Blue%2C%20Green%2C%20Pink%2C%20and%20Yellow%20colour%20options%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%20While%20pre-orders%20for%20the%20phones%20begin%20on%20September%2015%2C%20the%20iPhone%2015%20and%20iPhone%2015%20Plus%20will%20go%20on%20sale%20on%20September%2022.%20The%20handsets%20will%20be%20available%20with%20up%20to%20512GB%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EiPhone%2015%2C%20iPhone%2015%20Plus%20specifications%20and%20features%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20iPhone%2015%20is%20a%20dual%20SIM%20(Nano)%20smartphone%20that%20sports%20a%C2%A06.1-inch%20Super%20Retina%20XDR%20OLED%20display%20with%20Ceramic%20Shield%20material%20for%20additional%20protection.%20This%20year%2C%20Apple%20has%20also%20equipped%20the%20iPhone%2015%20with%20the%20Dynamic%20Island%20that%20was%20introduced%20on%20the%20iPhone%2014%20Pro%20models%20last%20year.%20The%20display%20offers%20up%20to%202000%20nits%20of%20peak%20brightness%20and%20the%20handset%20has%20an%20IP68%20rating%20for%20dust%20and%20water%20resistance.%20The%20iPhone%2015%20Plus%20has%20a%20larger%206.7-inch%C2%A0Super%20Retina%20XDR%20OLED%20display.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cimg%20data-dimension%3D%5C%221200x675%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22iphone%2015%20plus%20inline%20iphone%2015%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.gadgets3