Fstory%2Fstolen-van-gogh-painting-recovered-three-years-after-museum-raid-12959997%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fstolen-van-gogh-painting-recovered-three-years-after-museum-raid-12959997%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fstolen-van-gogh-painting-recovered-three-years-after-museum-raid-12959997%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20It's%20Catch-22%20But%20This%20Is%20Why%20BJP%2C%20JDS%20Need%20Each%20Other%20In%20Karnataka%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20have%20made%20their%20partnership%20official%20and%20the%20latter%20is%20set%20to%20join%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20ahead%20of%20next%20year's%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDetails%20about%20seat-sharing%20are%20still%20unclear%20at%20this%20time.%20Senior%20BJP%20leader%20BS%20Yediyurappa%20had%20claimed%20the%20smaller%20party%20will%20contest%20four%20seats%20but%20that%20was%20denied%20by%20JDS%20leader%20HD%20Kumaraswamy.%20He%20told%20NDTV%20%26quot%3Bdetails%20will%20be%20revealed%20after%20(next%20week's)%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20BJP%20won%2025%20seats.%20The%20JDS%20-%20then%20with%20the%20Congress%20-%20got%20one.%20Now%2C%20after%20a%20resounding%20defeat%20in%20the%202023%20Assembly%20election%20-%20the%20BJP%20won%2066%20seats%2C%20less%20than%20half%20the%20Congress'%20135%2C%20and%20the%20JDS%20its%20second-worst%20tally%20of%2019%20-%20the%20two%20defeated%20parties%20have%20joined%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELayering%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20results%20over%20the%20Assembly%20segments%20map%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%2018%2C%20the%20BJP%20eight%20and%20the%20JDS%20two.%20Maintaining%20a%20strong%20presence%20in%20Karnataka%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20BJP%20as%20it%20faces%20headwinds%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Maharashtra%20due%20to%20an%20exodus%20of%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EState%20election%20results%20may%20not%20necessarily%20be%20replicated%20in%20a%20general%20election%20since%20the%20'Modi%20factor'%20is%20likely%20to%20kick%20in%20for%20the%20BJP.%20In%20the%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20the%20reason%20for%2019%20per%20cent%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20according%20to%20Axis%20My%20India.%20That%20number%20was%20over%2050%20per%20cent%20for%20the%202019%20election%2C%20according%20to%20a%20survey%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20surveys%20predict%20a%20two-six%20seat%20loss%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20a%20corresponding%20decline%20of%20seven%20per%20cent%20vote%20share%2C%20as%20shown%20in%20the%20graph%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fv9vee66o_jds-bjp-tie-up_625x300_12_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EJDS-BJP%20tie-up%20before%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20Karnataka%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20upbeat%20and%20creating%20a%20pool%20of%20its%20own%20labharthis%2C%20or%20welfare%20beneficiaries%2C%20to%20counter%20the%20BJP's%20model%2C%20which%20is%20implemented%20by%20the%20centre.%20It%20now%20has%20Vokkaligas%20and%20Lingayats%20voting%20for%20it%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20AHINDA%20(marginalised%20classes%20and%20Muslims)%20creating%20a%20big%20social%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20local%20BJP%20unit%20is%20in%20disarray%20amid%20reports%20of%20intense%20factionalism.%20So%20much%20so%20it%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20able%20to%20name%20its%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20nominee%2C%20with%20the%20party%20returning%20charge%20to%20Mr%20Yediyurappa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20has%20even%20speculated%20the%20BJP%20may%20have%20decided%20to%20do%20the%20unthinkable%20and%20back%20Mr%20Kumaraswamy%20for%20the%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJDS%20patriarch%20and%20ex-Prime%20Minister%20Deve%20Gowda%20has%20said%20the%20decision%20to%20ally%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bessential%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bsave%26quot%3B%20the%20regional%20party.%20The%20alliance%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20mean%20JDS%20has%20nothing%20left...%20even%20the%20BJP%20should%20not%20think%20so.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20JDS%20is%20facing%20an%20existential%20crisis%20after%20its%20Assembly%20tally%20fell%20to%20half%2C%2019%20in%202023%20versus%2037%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20all%20of%20these%20-%2017%20seats%2C%20to%20be%20specific%20-%20were%20in%20traditional%20strongholds%20of%20Old%20Mysuru%20and%20Bengaluru.%20The%20JDS%20is%20now%20fearing%20an%20'Operation%20Haath'%20by%20the%20Congress%20targeting%20the%20few%20MLAs%20it%20has%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20'Operation%20Kamala'%20carried%20out%20by%20BJP%20to%20steal%20away%20rival%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMr%20Deve%20Gowda%20has%20claimed%20Siddaramaiah%20was%20conspiring%20to%20end%20the%20JDS%20in%20order%20to%20avenge%20a%202018%20election%20defeat%20against%20a%20JDS%20candidate%20and%20for%20developments%20that%20forced%20his%20explosion%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20JDS%20was%20also%20peeved%20at%20the%20Congress%20for%20not%20following%20coalition%20dharma%20and%20its%20inability%20to%20transfer%20votes%20to%20its%20candidates%20in%20the%202019%20election%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20defeat%20of%20Mr%20Deve%20Gowda%20from%20Tumkur%20and%20Mr%20Kumaraswmay's%20son%2C%20Nikhil%2C%20from%20Mandya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20didn't%20ally%20with%20the%20JDS%20in%202023%20and%20made%20a%20big%20dent%20in%20its%20Vokkaliga%20vote%20bank.%20The%20community%20support%20for%20the%20JDS%20fell%20by%2030%20per%20cent%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20the%20CSDS%2C%20and%2022%20per%20cent%20of%20this%20was%20lapped%20up%20by%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20pitched%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%2C%20who%20is%20a%20Vokkaliga%20leader%2C%20to%20compete%20directly%20with%20the%20Gowda%20family.%20Now%2C%20the%20JDS%20risks%20losing%20further%20support%20from%20the%20influential%20community%20as%20now%20even%20the%20Congress%20can%20make%20a%20Vokkaliga%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20will%20hope%20the%20JDS%20can%20transfer%20its%20Vokkaliga%20votes%20to%20the%20party%20and%20help%20it%20gain%20in%20southern%20Karnataka%20(Old%20Mysuru%20and%20Bengaluru%20regions).%20As%20a%20trade-off%2C%20the%20JDS%20will%20hope%20for%20Brahmin%2C%20Lingayat%20and%20some%20OBC%20votes%20that%20should%20compensate%20for%20the%20loss%20of%20minority%2C%20tribal%20and%20Dalit%20voters%20to%20the%20Congress.%20Both%20parties%20gain%20in%20the%20short%20term%2C%20though%20trust%20deficit%20exists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20needs%20to%20maintain%20its%20tally%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20it%20also%20needs%20allies%20in%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20India%20to%20show%20its%20acceptability%20to%20voters.%20And%2C%20as%20Mr%20Deve%20Gowda%20said%2C%20the%20JDS%20needs%20the%20BJP%20for%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20a%20Catch-22%20situation%20for%20the%20JDS%20as%20the%20BJP%20may%20aim%20for%20a%20permanent%20steal%2C%20or%20even%20a%20temporary%20dent%2C%20in%20the%20socialist%20party's%20vote%20base.%20It%20cannot%2C%20after%20all%2C%20brush%20aside%20the%20risk%20of%20another%20Shiv%20Sena-type%20strike%20in%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20aggressive%20push%20in%20the%20Old%20Mysuru%20region%20-%20where%20it%20gained%20vote%20share%20and%20helped%20the%20Congress%20win%20more%20seats%20-%20harmed%20the%20JDS%20in%20the%202023%20election.%20The%20historically%20frosty%20relationship%20of%20power%20transfer%20in%202007%20has%20an%20overhang%20on%20this%20renewed%20friendship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20need%20of%20the