f%20Worldwide%20says%20people%20in%20the%20earthquake%20zone%20are%20traumatised%20and%20helpless.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A77%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-africa-66790363%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Poetry%20Offers%20Pleasure%20and%20Solace%2C%20and%20Sensitises%20on%20Pain%20and%20Deprivation%20of%20the%20World%3A%20Javed%20Akhtar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F11121248%2FJaved_Akhtar.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJaved%20Akhtar%20was%20given%20an%20honorary%20degree%20by%20the%20School%20of%20Oriental%20and%20African%20Studies%20in%20London%2C%20on%20September%207.%20Reproduced%20below%20is%20the%20full%20text%20of%20his%20speech.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELord%20Hastings%20Chair%20of%20the%20Board%20of%20Trustees%20of%20SOAS%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Zeinab%20Badawi%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDirector%2C%20Professor%20Adam%20Habib%20and%20Graduents%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stand%20humbled%20for%20the%20honour%20bestowed%20on%20me%20and%20thank%20you%20for%20making%20me%20a%20Fellow%20of%20SOAS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20such%20an%20award%20is%20bestowed%2C%C2%A0we%C2%A0must%20not%20forget%20that%20it%20is%20the%20art%20that%20is%20being%20honoured%20and%20not%20the%20artist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20people%20who%20wonder%20why%20poetry%20should%20be%20honoured%20in%20the%20time%20of%20science%20and%20technology.%20I%20think%20before%20taking%20the%20final%20call%2C%20we%20should%20give%20a%20thought%20to%20what%20is%20poetry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20rhyme%20and%20metre%20do%20not%20make%20poetry.%20I%20am%20talking%20of%20good%20poetry%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20believe%20good%20poetry%20is%20born%20in%20a%20paradox%2C%20of%20complete%20awareness%20and%20complete%20submergence%2C%20complete%20passion%20and%20complete%20craft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGood%20poetry%20is%20born%20in%20a%20no%20man%E2%80%99s%20land%20between%20the%20conscious%20and%20the%20subconscious.%20It%20comes%20from%20the%20depth%20of%20the%20poet%E2%80%99s%20psyche%2C%20consciousness%2C%20sense%20of%20values%2C%20and%20that%20is%20why%20it%20holds%20magic%2C%20charm%2C%20and%20connects%20to%20the%20reader%E2%80%99s%20subconscious%2C%20conscience%20and%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELadies%20and%20gentlemen%2C%20we%20are%20living%20in%20the%20era%20of%20post-truth%20where%20we%20arrive%20at%20conclusions%20before%20searching%20for%20logic%20and%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20favourable%20laws%20for%20the%20powerful%20corporates%20are%20called%20effort%20for%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20any%20effort%20to%20save%20the%20environment%20is%20called%20blocking%20the%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20greed%20to%20take%20over%20oil%20resources%20of%20some%20places%20is%20called%20war%20on%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubjugating%C2%A0and%20stripping%20a%C2%A0woman%C2%A0of%20all%20her%20rights%C2%A0is%20called%20protecting%C2%A0her%C2%A0dignity%20and%20chastity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20hating%20the%20minorities%20is%20the%20ultimate%20proof%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20patriotism%20and%20nationalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20living%20in%20a%20world%20where%20all%20the%20means%20of%20information%20and%20communication%20are%2C%20one%20after%20another%2C%20falling%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20powerful.%20We%20are%20living%20in%20a%20world%20where%20many%20people%20are%20discontent%2C%20unhappy%20and%20frustrated%20and%20that%20is%20why%20they%20are%20looking%20towards%20religion%20or%20its%20second%20line%20of%20defence%20%E2%80%93%20spiritualism%20and%20sufism.%20One%20must%20accept%20these%20pursuits%20provide%20some%20solace%20to%20some%20people%20by%20making%20them%20look%20away%20from%20day%20to%20day%20realities.%20They%20give%20you%20painkillers%20to%20relieve%20your%20pain%2C%20not%20to%20heal%20the%20injury%2C%20they%20never%20challenge%20the%20status%20quo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20poetry%20provides%20you%20with%20the%20music%20of%20language%2C%20pleasure%20and%20solace.%20But%20at%20the%20same%20time%20sensitises%20you%20to%20the%20pain%20and%20deprivation%20of%20the%20world.%20Take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20poets%20of%20the%2020th%20century%2C%20from%20one%20end%20of%20the%20world%20to%20another%2C%20you%20will%20see%20poets%20have%20turned%20their%20pens%20into%20swords%2C%20to%20battle%20the%20evil%20forces%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBe%20it%20Pablo%20Neruda%20of%20Chile%2C%20Mehmoud%20Darvesh%20of%20Palestine%2C%20Breyten%20of%20South%20Africa%2C%20Nazrul%20from%20Bengal%2C%20Faiz%20from%20Punjab%20and%20Majaz%20from%20Avadh%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20it%20just%20a%20coincidence%20that%20fascist%C2%A0ideologies%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20produce%20one%20major%20poet%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20because%20poetry%20is%20the%20language%20of%20love%2Fpeace%2Fjustice%20and%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAre%20such%20poets%20required%20today%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20a%20big%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EActually%20with%20great%20pride%20I%20would%20like%20to%20share%20that%20in%20India%2C%20in%20the%20late%2030s%2C%20%C2%A0a%20pan-Indian%20Progressive%20Writers%20Movement%20was%20started%20in%20which%20authors%20and%20poets%20passed%20a%20resolution%20to%20undertake%20the%20responsibility%20to%20write%20against%20colonialism%2C%20economic%20exploitation%20and%20support%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20movement%20created%20great%20literature%20but%20I%20have%20reservations%20about%20the%20word%20responsibility.%20Responsibility%20is%20most%20often%20an%20imposition.%20I%20believe%20it%20is%20not%20the%20duty%20but%20the%20right%20of%20every%20writer%20and%20poet%20to%20raise%20their%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hope%20that%20such%20patronage%20and%20felicitation%C2%A0of%20poets%20and%20writers%20will%20encourage%20them%20to%20fully%20claim%20their%20right%20to%C2%A0speak%20and%20write%C2%A0and%20challenge%20the%20status%20quo%C2%A0to%C2%A0usher%20in%20a%20new%C2%A0social%20order%C2%A0in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThank%20you%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJaved%20Akhtar%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694536207000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fpoetry-offers-pleasure-and-solace-and-sensitises-on-pain-and-deprivation-of-the-world-javed-akhtar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Is%20it%20just%20a%20coincidence%20that%20fascist%C2%A0ideologies%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20produce%20one%20major%20poet%3F%C2%A0That%20is%20because%20poetry%20is%20the%20language%20of%20love%2Fpeace%2Fjustice%20and%20equality.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Moroccans%20who%20survived%20earthquake%20now%20bracing%20for%20the%20cold%20and%20rain%20of%20winter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694536200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F768x432%2Fskynews-moulay-brahim-morocco_6282683.jpg%3F20230912180956%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmorocco-earthquake-those-who-survived-the-earthquake-are-now-bracing-for-the-cold-and-rain-of-winter-12959978%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20a%20distance%20the%20town%20of%20Moulay%20Brahim%20looks%20pretty%20much%20abandoned.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A63%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmorocco-earthquake-those-who-survived-the-earthquake-are-now-bracing-for-the-cold-and-rain-of-winter-12959978%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmorocco-earthquake-those-who-survived-the-earthquake-are-now-bracing-for-the-cold-and-rain-of-winter-12959978%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmorocco-eart