y%20Justice%20PV%20Kunhikrishnan%20came%20while%20cancelling%20a%20case%20of%20obscenity%20under%20Section%20292%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20against%20a%2033-year-old%20man%20who%20was%20back%20in%202016%20caught%20by%20police%20while%20watching%20porn%20videos%20on%20his%20mobile%20phone%20on%20the%20roadside%20near%20the%20Aluva%20palace%20in%20Kochi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20and%20ruling%20came%20on%20the%20accused%20person's%20plea%20to%20cancel%20the%20FIR%20and%20the%20court%20proceedings%20against%20him%20in%20connection%20with%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20pornography%20was%20in%20practice%20for%20centuries%20and%20the%20new%20digital%20age%20has%20made%20it%20more%20accessible%2C%20even%20to%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20question%20to%20be%20decided%20in%20this%20case%20is%20whether%20a%20person%20watching%20a%20porn%20video%20in%20his%20private%20time%20without%20exhibiting%20it%20to%20others%20amounts%20to%20an%20offence%3F%20A%20court%20of%20law%20cannot%20declare%20that%20the%20same%20amounts%20to%20an%20offence%20for%20the%20simple%20reason%20that%20it%20is%20his%20private%20choice%20and%20interference%20with%20the%20same%20amounts%20to%20an%20intrusion%20of%20his%20privacy%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20there%20was%20no%20allegation%20that%20the%20petitioner%20(accused)%20publicly%20exhibited%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20of%20the%20considered%20opinion%20that%20watching%20an%20obscene%20photo%20by%20a%20person%20in%20his%20privacy%20by%20itself%20is%20not%20an%20offence%20under%20Section%20292%20(obscenity)%20of%20IPC.%20Similarly%2C%20watching%20an%20obscene%20video%20by%20a%20person%20from%20a%20mobile%20phone%20in%20his%20privacy%20is%20also%20not%20an%20offence%20under%20Section%20292%20IPC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20accused%20is%20trying%20to%20circulate%20or%20distribute%20or%20publicly%20exhibit%20any%20obscene%20video%20or%20photos%2C%20then%20the%20offence%20under%20Section%20292%20IPC%20is%20attracted%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Kunhikrishnan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20no%20offence%20under%20Section%20292%20of%20the%20IPC%20is%20made%20out%20against%20the%20accused%2C%20the%20court%20said%20and%20cancelled%20all%20the%20proceedings%20in%20the%20magisterial%20court%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Justice%20Kunhikrishnan%20also%20cautioned%20parents%20against%20giving%20mobile%20phones%20with%20internet%20access%20to%20children%20to%20make%20them%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20parents%20should%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20danger%20behind%20it.%20Let%20the%20children%20watch%20informative%20news%20and%20videos%20from%20the%20mobile%20phones%20of%20their%20parents%20in%20their%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BParents%20should%20never%20hand%20over%20mobile%20phones%20to%20minor%20children%20to%20make%20them%20happy%20and%20thereafter%20complete%20their%20daily%20routine%20works%20in%20their%20house%20allowing%20unsupervised%20use%20of%20mobile%20phones%20by%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kunhikrishnan%20said%20that%20if%20minor%20children%20end%20up%20watching%20porn%20videos%2C%20which%20are%20now%20accessible%20in%20all%20mobile%20phones%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20will%20be%20far%20reaching%20consequences%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20the%20children%20play%20cricket%20or%20football%20or%20other%20games%20they%20like%20during%20their%20leisure%20time.%20That%20is%20necessary%20for%20a%20healthy%20young%20generation%20who%20are%20to%20become%20the%20beacons%20of%20hope%20of%20our%20nation%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20purchasing%20food%20from%20restaurants%20through%20%E2%80%98swiggy'%20and%20%E2%80%98zomato'%2C%20let%20the%20children%20taste%20the%20delicious%20food%20made%20by%20their%20mother%20and%20let%20the%20children%20play%20at%20playgrounds%20and%20come%20back%20home%20to%20the%20mesmerising%20smell%20of%20their%20mother's%20food.%20I%20leave%20it%20there%20to%20the%20wisdom%20of%20the%20parents%20of%20minor%20children%20of%20this%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694532960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-09%2F1482fqp_kerala-high-court-650_625x300_05_September_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-high-court-cancels-case-against-man-caught-watching-porn-private-choice-4383572%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Watching%20pornographic%20photographs%20or%20videos%20in%20one's%20private%20time%20without%20showing%20it%20to%20others%20is%20not%20an%20offence%20under%20the%20law%20as%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20personal%20choice%2C%20the%20Kerala%20High%20Court%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-high-court-cancels-case-against-man-caught-watching-porn-private-choice-4383572%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Law%20Not%20To%20Create%20Army%20Of%20Idle%20People%3A%20Court%20Rejects%20Maintenance%20Appeal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EObserving%20that%20the%20law%20for%20providing%20maintenance%20to%20a%20spouse%20is%20not%20meant%20to%20create%20an%20army%20of%20idle%20people%20waiting%20for%20a%20dole%20by%20the%20estranged%20partner%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20Tuesday%20refused%20to%20direct%20a%20man%20to%20pay%20maintenance%20to%20his%20wife%20who%20is%20herself%20earning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20said%20in%20addition%20to%20being%20qualified%2C%20the%20woman%20was%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20doubt%20there%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20%E2%80%98capacity'%20and%20%E2%80%98actual%20earning'%2C%20but%20here%20it%20is%20not%20a%20case%20where%20the%20appellant%20(woman)%20had%20only%20the%20capacity%20but%20the%20document%20on%20record%20clearly%20point%20out%20that%20she%20has%20also%20been%20working%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Suresh%20Kumar%20Kait%20and%20Neena%20Bansal%20Krishna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20dismissed%20the%20woman's%20appeal%20challenging%20a%20family%20court's%20order%20by%20which%20her%20plea%20seeking%20maintenance%20from%20her%20estranged%20husband%20was%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20referred%20to%20a%20previous%20judgment%20of%20another%20high%20court%20in%20which%20was%20observed%20that%20Section%2024%20(Maintenance%20pendente%20lite%20and%20expenses%20of%20proceedings)%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%20(HMA)%20has%20been%20enacted%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20providing%20monetary%20assistance%20to%20either%20spouse%20who%20is%20incapable%20of%20supporting%20himself%20or%20herself%20in%20spite%20of%20sincere%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaintenance%20pendente%20lite%20provides%20for%20the%20claimant%20spouse's%20support%20as%20well%20as%20the%20costs%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20law%20does%20not%20expect%20persons%20engaged%20in%20the%20legal%20battles%20to%20remain%20idle%20solely%20with%20the%20objective%20of%20squeezing%20out%20money%20from%20the%20opposite%20party.%20Section%2024%20of%20HMA%20is%20not%20meant%20to%20create%20an%20Army%20of%20idle%20people%20waiting%20for%20a%20dole%20to%20be%20awarded%20by%20the%20other%20spouse%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20noted%20as%20being%20said%20in%20the%20judgment%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20the%20woman%20sought%20an%20interim%20maintenance%20of%20Rs%2035%2C000%20per%20month%20in%20addition%20to%20litigation%20expenses%20of%20Rs%2055%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20woman%20was%20an%20M.Phil%20at%20the%20time%20of%20her%20marriage%20and%20now%20she%20held%20a%20Ph.D%20(Management)%20with%20professional%20qualification%20in%20computers%20and%20was%20also%20working%2C%20whereas%20the%20man%20is%20a%20simple%20graduate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20not%20only%20is%20the%20woman%20highly%20qualified%20but%20had%20been%20working%20even%20at%20the%20time%20of%20her%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20principal%20judge%2C%20family%20court%20has%20rightly%20observed%20that%20the%20appellant%20(woman)%20had%20initially%20failed%20to%20disclose%20that%20she%20was%20working%20even%20if%20not%20regularly%20or%20for%20charity%20as%20claimed%20by%20her.%20She%20had%20failed%20to%20disclose%20any%20of%20these%20facts%20and%20was%20compelled%20to%20do%20so%20after%20the%20filing%20of%20the%20application%20%E2%80%A6%20It%20was%20also%20observed%20by%20the%20principal%20judge%2C%20family%20court%20that%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20accept%20that%20a%20person%20who%20is%20so%20highly%20qualified%20would%20not%20be%20working%20and%20it%20is%20even%20more%20difficult%20to%20accept%20that%20she%20would%20be%20working%20for%20charity%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20the%20documents%20and%20the%20admissions%20made%20by%20the%20woman%20clearly%20lead%20to%20an%20irresistible%20conclusion%20that%20she%20is%20employed%20in%20the%20office%20of%20a%20legislator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20find%20that%20in%20the%20present%20case%20it%20is%20not%20only%20that%20the%20appellant%20(woman)%20is%20highly%20qualified%20and%20has%20an%20earning%20capacity%2C%20but%20in%20fact%20she%20has%20been%20earning%2C%20though%20has%20not%20been%20inclined%20to%20truthfully%20disclose%20her%20true%20income.%20Such%20a%20person%20cannot%20be%20held%20entitled%20to%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPertinently%2C%20the%20claim%20for%20maintenance%20by%20the%20appellant%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20Protection%20of%20Women%20against%20Domestic%20Violence%20Act%20has%20also%20met%20the%20same%20fate%20and%20the%20maintenance%20has%20been%20declined%20to%20her.%20We%2C%20therefore%2C%20find%20no%20merit%20in%20the%20appeal%20which%20is%20hereby%20dismissed%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694532960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-02%2Fdelhi-high-court_650x400_41454944412.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flaw-not-to-create-army-of-idle-people-court-rejects-maintenance-appeal-4383602%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Observing%20that%20the%20law%20for%20providing%20maintenance%20to%20a%20spouse%20is%20not%20meant%20to%20create%20an%20army%20of%20idle%20people%20waiting%20for%20a%20dole%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20Tuesday%20refused%20to%20direct%20a%20man%20to%20pay%20maintenance%20to%20his%20wife%20who%20is%20herself%20earning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flaw-not-to-create-army-of-idle-people-court-rejects-maintenance-appeal-4383602%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flaw-not-to-create-army-of-idle-people-court-rejects-maintenance-appeal-4383602%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flaw-not-to-create-army-of-idle-people-court-rejects-maintenance-appeal-4383602%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22River%20of%20red%20wine%20floods%20Portuguese%20village%20after%20distillery%20mishap%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694532136000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FB5A0%2Fproduction%2F_131069464_p0gd4hjm.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F