%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20that%20they%20filed%20prior%20to%20contesting%20their%20last%20elections%20and%20subsequent%20by-elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFour%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20one%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20are%20vacant%2C%20while%20four%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seats%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20are%20undefined%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20added%20that%20the%20affidavits%20of%20one%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20three%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20could%20not%20be%20analysed%20as%20they%20were%20not%20available.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cb%3E40%25%20sitting%20MPs%20have%20declared%20criminal%20cases%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20has%20found%20that%20306%20of%20the%20763%20(40%25)%20sitting%20MPs%20analysed%20have%20declared%20criminal%20cases%20against%20themselves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELakshadweep%20leads%20the%20states%20and%20union%20territories%20with%20the%20highest%20proportion%20of%20MPs%20with%20criminal%20cases%2C%20as%20its%20lone%20MP%20has%20declared%20criminal%20cases%20against%20himself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20followed%20by%20Kerala%2C%20where%2023%20out%20of%2029%20MPs%20(79%25)%20have%20criminal%20cases.%20Bihar%20(73%25)%20is%20next%20with%2041%20of%2056%20MPs%2C%20followed%20by%20Maharashtra%20(57%25)%20with%2037%20of%2065%20MPs%2C%20Telangana%20(54%25)%20with%2013%20out%20of%2024%20MPs%20and%20Delhi%20(50%25)%20with%20five%20out%20of%20its%20ten%20MPs%20having%20declared%20criminal%20cases%20against%20themselves%20in%20their%20affidavits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20also%20found%20that%20194%20of%20these%20sitting%20MPs%20(25%25)%20have%20serious%20criminal%20cases%2C%20including%20kidnapping%2C%20murder%2C%20attempt%20to%20murder%2C%20crimes%20against%20women%2C%20etc.%20against%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20terms%20of%20MPs%20with%20serious%20criminal%20cases%2C%20Lakshadweep%20again%20leads%20with%20100%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20followed%20by%20Bihar%20(50%25)%2C%20where%2028%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%2056%20MPs%20have%20serious%20criminal%20cases%20against%20them.%20After%20it%20come%20Telangana%20(38%25)%20with%20nine%20out%20of%2024%20MPs%2C%20Kerala%20(34%25)%20with%20ten%20out%20of%2029%20MPs%2C%20Maharashtra%20(34%25)%20with%2022%20out%20of%2065%20MPs%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(34%25)%20with%2037%20out%20of%20108%20MPs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERJD%20has%20most%20number%20of%20MPs%20with%20criminal%20cases%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20found%20that%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20has%20the%20highest%20percentage%20of%20MPs%20with%20criminal%20cases.%20Five%20out%20of%20six%2C%20or%2083%25%20MPs%20from%20the%20party%2C%20have%20criminal%20cases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20followed%20by%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20(CPI(M))%20with%2075%25%20or%20six%20out%20of%20eight%20MPs%2C%20the%20Congress%20(53%25)%20with%2043%20out%20of%2081%20MPs%2C%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20(YSCRP)%20(42%25)%20with%2013%20out%20of%2031%20MPs%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(AITC)%20(39%25)%20with%2014%20out%20of%2036%20MPs%2C%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20(38%25)%20with%20two%20out%20of%20eight%20MPs%2C%20the%20BJP%20(36%25)%20with%20139%20out%20of%20385%20MPs%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20(27%25)%20with%20three%20out%20of%2011%20MPs%20having%20criminal%20cases%20against%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20party-wise%20terms%20of%20MPs%20with%20serious%20criminal%20cases%2C%20the%20RJD%20again%20leads%20with%2050%25%20or%20three%20out%20of%20its%20six%20MPs%20having%20serious%20criminal%20cases%20against%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felection-commission-candidates-criminal-past%5C%22%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20Not%20Much%20to%20Celebrate%20in%20EC%20Saying%20Candidates%20Have%20to%20Declare%20Criminal%20Records%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20followed%20by%20the%20YSRCP%20(35%25)%20with%2011%20out%20of%2031%20MPs%2C%20the%20Congress%20(32%25)%20with%2026%20out%20of%2081%20MPs%2C%20the%20NCP%20(25%25)%20with%20two%20out%20of%20eight%20MPs%2C%20the%20CPI(M)%20(also%2025%25)%20with%20two%20out%20of%20eight%20MPs%2C%20the%20AITC%20(19%25)%20with%20seven%20out%20of%2036%20MPs%20and%20the%20AAP%20(9%25)%20with%20one%20out%20of%2011%20MPs%20having%20serious%20criminal%20cases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20said%20serious%20criminal%20cases%20include%20offences%20for%20which%20the%20maximum%20punishment%20is%20five%20years%20or%20more%3B%20if%20an%20offence%20is%20non-bailable%3B%20if%20it%20is%20an%20electoral%20offence%20(bribery%2C%20for%20example)%3B%20offences%20related%20to%20loss%20to%20exchequer%3B%20offences%20that%20are%20assault%2C%20murder%2C%20kidnap%20or%20rape-related%3B%20offences%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%20(Section%208)%3B%20offences%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%3B%20and%20crimes%20against%20women.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%2011%20sitting%20MPs%20have%20declared%20cases%20relating%20to%20murder%2C%2032%20MPs%20have%20cases%20relating%20to%20attempt%20to%20murder%20and%2021%20MPs%20have%20cases%20relating%20to%20crimes%20against%20women%2C%20of%20which%20four%20MPs%20have%20declared%20cases%20related%20to%20rape.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20has%20most%20MPs%20with%20murder%2C%20attempt%20to%20murder%20cases%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20terms%20of%20states%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20has%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20MPs%20(three)%20with%