ea%20of%20Chutnefy%2C%20the%20duo%20recalls%2C%20came%20to%20Prasanna.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20enter%20the%20food%20industry%20and%20the%20idea%20of%20making%20a%20chutney%20brand%20was%20something%20I%20was%20mulling%20on%20for%20a%20while%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20markets%2C%20we%20only%20see%20salsas%2C%20peri%20peri%20and%20other%20sauces%20but%20India%20has%20its%20own%20range%20of%20it%20that%20is%20not%20that%20common.%20I%20wanted%20to%20reintroduce%20them%20in%20the%20market%20in%20a%20ready-to-make%20form.%20The%20larger%20goal%20was%20also%20to%20introduce%20it%20to%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20thought%20that%20eventually%20led%20to%20Chutnefy%E2%80%99s%205-second%20chutneys.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20the%20idea%20very%20interesting%20and%20decided%20to%20quit%20my%20career%20as%20a%20banker%20and%20joined%20Prasanna%20in%20this%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shreyas%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20tangy%20and%20spicy%20journey%20towards%20delicious%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20started%20to%20work%20on%20their%20idea%20two%20years%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20set%20up%20a%20research%20and%20development%20centre%20in%20Ambattur%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20had%20a%20team%20of%20scientists%2C%20technologists%20and%20culinary%20experts%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20to%20simplify%20chutney-making%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prasanna%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20things%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20tackle%20with%20chutneys%20were%20to%20shorten%20the%20time%20of%20preparation%20as%20it%20takes%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20chopping%2C%20mixing%20and%20blending.%20Secondly%2C%20we%20also%20wanted%20to%20address%20the%20quantity%20issues.%20In%20households%2C%20chutney%20is%20never%20made%20for%20one%20person.%20But%20we%20prepared%20our%20chutney%20in%20smaller%20batches