9s%20attempt%20to%20keep%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20the%20capital%20from%20being%20monopolised%20by%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20global%20press%20fixated%20on%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwatered%20down%E2%80%9D%20declaration%20that%20they%20say%20failed%20to%20adequately%20address%20Russia%20as%20an%20aggressor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKyiv%2C%20too%2C%20had%20a%20harsh%20reaction%20with%20Ukraine%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20minister%20Oleg%20Nikolenko%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20grateful%20to%20the%20partners%20who%20tried%20to%20include%20strong%20wording%20in%20the%20text.%20However%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20aggression%20against%20Ukraine%2C%20G20%20has%20nothing%20to%20be%20proud%20of%2C%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EG20%20adopted%20a%20final%20declaration.%20We%20are%20grateful%20to%20the%20partners%20who%20tried%20to%20include%20strong%20wording%20in%20the%20text.%20However%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20aggression%20against%20Ukraine%2C%20G20%20has%20nothing%20to%20be%20proud%20of.%20This%20is%20how%20the%20main%20elements%20of%20the%20text%20could%20look%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20reality%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqZqYluVKKS%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FqZqYluVKKS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Oleg%20Nikolenko%20(%40OlegNikolenko_)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FOlegNikolenko_%2Fstatus%2F1700507183467602175%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%209%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%5BModi%5D%20wrapped%20up%20Sunday%20a%20G20%20summit%20that%20played%20down%20deep%20divisions%20over%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20climate%20change%2C%20but%20gave%20him%20a%20moment%20in%20the%20diplomatic%20spotlight.%20Facing%20a%20major%20diplomatic%20embarrassment%2C%20host%20India%20pressed%20members%20to%20agree%20to%20a%20common%20statement%20on%20Saturday%20that%20denounced%20the%20use%20of%20force%20for%20territorial%20gain%2C%20but%20shied%20away%20from%20direct%20criticism%20of%20Russia%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20report%20in%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kyivpost.com%2Fpost%2F21473%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKyiv%20Post%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrance%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lemonde.fr%2Fen%2Fopinion%2Farticle%2F2023%2F09%2F11%2Fthe-g20-in-new-delhi-a-summit-without-major-results_6132551_23.html%5C%22%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELe%20Monde%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ecalled%20the%20event%20%E2%80%9Cprofitable%20for%20the%20organiser%E2%80%9D%20but%20said%20that%20the%20summit%20%E2%80%9Cdid%20little%20to%20mask%20the%20disappointment%20of%20the%20final%20statement%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%5BModi%5D%20had%20persuaded%20Indonesia%20to%20swap%20for%202022%20in%20order%20to%20stage%20this%20prestigious%20gathering%20as%20close%20as%20possible%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20general%20elections%2C%20scheduled%20for%202024.%20He%20has%20already%20taken%2C%20and%20will%20certainly%20continue%20to%20take%2C%20good%20advantage%20of%20this%20opportunity%2C%20using%20it%20to%20play%20on%20national%20pride.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20unquestionable%20personal%20success%2C%20despite%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20Chinese%20and%20Russian%20presidents%2C%20did%20little%20to%20mask%20the%20disappointment%20of%20the%20final%20statement%2C%20the%20balance%20sought%20in%20a%20world%20that%20the%20G20%20partly%20represents.%20This%20disappointment%20was%20evident%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Ukraine.%20The%20war%20waged%20by%20Russia%20since%20February%202022%20receives%20only%20a%20short%20passage%2C%20distinctly%20lower%20down%20on%20the%20statement%20issued%20at%20the%20previous%20G20%20summit%20in%20Bali%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20being%20asked%20about%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20Bali%20declaration%20and%20the%20New%20Delhi%20one%2C%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20nonchalantly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fbali-was-bali-and-new-delhi-is-new-delhi-jaishankar-on-reference-to-ukraine-in-g-20-declaration%2Farticle67289990.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%2522With%2520regard%2520to%2520the%2520comparison%2Cthings%2520have%2520happened%2520since%2520then.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CBali%20is%20Bali%20and%20New%20Delhi%20is%20New%20Delhi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20French%20newspaper%20also%20called%20the%20declaration%20a%20disappointment%20on%20the%20climate%20front.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20disappointment%20is%20just%20as%20great%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20combating%20climate%20change.%20Despite%20the%20recent%20devastating%20succession%20of%20climate%20tragedies%2C%20the%20final%20statement%20fails%20to%20mention%20the%20objective%20of%20phasing%20out%20fossil%20fuels.%20Yet%20scientists%20consider%20this%20to%20be%20the%20only%20response%20capable%20of%20reversing%20a%20destructive%20curve%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcivil-society-calls-out-g20-declarations-omission-of-civic-space-erosion-democracy-decline%5C%22%3ECivil%20Society%20Calls%20Out%20G20%20Declaration%E2%80%99s%20Omission%20of%20Civic%20Space%20Erosion%2C%20Democracy%20Decline%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20outcome%20obviously%20reflects%20India%E2%80%99s%20rigid%20determination%20not%20to%20take%20sides%20in%20the%20war%2C%20but%20it%20is%20extraordinary%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20countries%20at%20the%20G20%20that%20do%20oppose%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20war%20of%20conquest%20were%20so%20prepared%20to%20be%20muzzled%20by%20the%20minority%20that%20%5Bthey%5D%20prefer%20to%20look%20away.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20UK%20official%20said%20the%20joint%20declaration%2C%20widely%20seen%20as%20weak%2C%20was%20in%20fact%20effective%20at%20putting%20pressure%20on%20Moscow.%20%E2%80%98By%20achieving%20consensus%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20G20%20has%20forced%20%5BVladimir%5D%20Putin%20to%20commit%20to%20a%20cessation%20of%20attacks%20on%20infrastructure%2C%20to%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20troops%20and%20to%20the%20return%20of%20territory%2C%E2%80%99%20they%20said.%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Fsep%2F10%2Fwatered-down-g20-statement-on-ukraine-is-sign-of-indias-growing-influence%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGuardian%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20end%20of%20the%20summit%20was%20marked%20by%20another%20disappointment%2C%20though%20this%20one%20was%20less%20global%20in%20nature.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20word%20spread%20that%20%5BModi%5D%20was%20to%20address%20the%203%2C000%20journalists%20at%20the%20G20%20media%20centre%20late%20on%20Sunday%2C%20a%20ripple%20of%20excitement%20spread%20through%20the%20venue.%20TV%20broadcasters%20started%20dedicating%20live%20coverage%20to%20showing%20an%20empty%20walkway%20where%20Mr%20Modi%20might%20emerge%20at%20%E2%80%98any%20moment%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shweta%20Sharma%20wrote%20for%20UK%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fasia%2Findia%2Fmodi-media-g20-india-press-freedom-b2409090.html%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndependent%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%2C%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20was%20not%20true