Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDarjeeling%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E3rd%C2%A0April%201897.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDear%20Miss%20Noble%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20have%20just%20found%20a%20bit%20of%20important%20work%20for%20you%20to%20do%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20downtrodden%20masses%20of%20India.%20The%20gentleman%20I%20take%20the%20liberty%20of%20introducing%20to%20you%20is%20in%20England%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Tiyas%20(Ezhavas)%2C%20a%20plebian%20caste%20in%20the%20native%20state%20of%20Malabar.%20You%20will%20realize%20from%20this%20gentleman%20what%20an%20amount%20of%20tyranny%20there%20is%20over%20these%20poor%20people%2C%20simply%20because%20of%20their%20caste.%20The%20Indian%20government%20has%20refused%20to%20interfere%20on%20grounds%20of%20non-interference%20in%20the%20internal%20administration%20of%20a%20native%20State.%20The%20only%20hope%20of%20these%20people%20is%20the%20English%20parliament.%20Do%20kindly%20everything%20in%20your%20power%20to%20help%20this%20matter%20%5Bin%5D%20being%20brought%20before%20the%20British%20public.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEver%20yours%20in%20the%20truth%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EVivekananda.%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E(%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Complete%20Works%20of%20Swami%20Vivekananda%3Cem%3E%2C%20Vol%20IX%2C%20Page%2095%2C%20quoted%20in%20%3C%2Fem%3EVivekananda%2C%20the%20Philosopher%20of%20Freedom%3Cem%3E%20p.%20393)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20letter%20to%20friend-disciple%20Margaret%20Noble%20(later%20with%20the%20monastic%20name%20Sister%20Nivedita)%20demonstrates%20certain%20aspects%20of%20Swami%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20outlook%3A%20the%20importance%20he%20placed%20on%20anti-caste%20activities%20and%20his%20belief%20that%20social%20justice%20denied%20for%20the%20lower%20castes%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20an%20internal%20issue%20of%20Indians%20or%20Hindus%20%E2%80%93%20a%20pointer%20on%20his%20attitude%20towards%20the%20west.%20The%20discrimination%20against%20Ezhavas%20did%20get%20raised%20in%20the%20British%20parliament%20on%20the%20July%2019%2C%201897%20through%20Herbert%20Roberts%2C%20a%20Liberal%20MP%2C%20then%20in%20the%20opposition.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20communication%20between%20Vivekananda%20and%20Dr%20Padmanabhan%20Palpu%2C%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20remarkable%20lower%20caste%20Ezhava%20politico-cultural%2C%20and%20socio-economic%20awakening%2C%20and%20translations%20of%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20work%20by%20Ezhava%20poet%20and%20social%20reformer%2C%20Kumaran%20Asan%2C%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Vivekananda%20lingered%20on%20in%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20common%20memory%20as%20a%20progressive%2C%20anti-caste%2C%20socialist-minded%2C%20modernity-inspired%20%3Cem%3Evedantin%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20can%20hardly%20be%20said%20of%20most%20of%20north%20India%2C%20where%20Vivekananda%20is%20the%20most%20used%20icon%20of%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20a%20space%20evacuated%20by%20liberals%20and%20seculars%2C%20abandoned%20by%20nuanced%20scholarship%2C%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20seems%20to%20have%20created%20a%20symbol%20emptied%20out%20of%20its%20historical%2C%20political%20and%20ethical%20content%20but%20naturalised%20through%20propagandist%20rituals%20repeated%20inexorably.%20Govind%20Krishnan%20V.%20is%20trying%20to%20evaluate%20this%20claim%20of%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20in%20his%20recently%20published%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EVivekananda%2C%20the%20Philosopher%20of%20Freedom%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Epublished%20by%20Aleph%20Books.%20Govind%E2%80%99s%20task%20becomes%20particularly%20daunting%20because%20a%20body%20of%20recent%20scholarship%2C%20coming%20from%20parts%20of%20the%20left%20and%20the%20marginalised%2C%20echo%20the%20Hindutva%20views%20on%20the%20man.%20Given%20the%20available%20narratives%2C%20Govind%20tries%20to%20create%20a%20third%20narrative%20to%20establish%20how%20Vivekananda%20is%20not%20just%20outside%20inclusive%2C%20egalitarian%20political%20thought%20and%20social%20action%20but%20should%20be%20a%20beacon%20of%20it.%20The%20book%E2%80%99s%20reiteration%20on%20the%20anti-Sangh%20nature%20of%20Vivekananda%20becomes%20an%20act%20in%20reclaiming%20his%20legacy%2C%20almost%20making%20it%20one%20to%20inherit%2C%20reminding%20us%20of%20Walter%20Benjamin%E2%80%99s%20observation%20in%20%3Cem%3EOn%20the%20Concept%20of%20History%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20historian%20capable%20of%20fanning%20the%20spark%20of%20hope%20in%20the%20past%20is%20the%20one%20who%20is%20firmly%20convinced%20that%20even%20the%20dead%20will%20not%20be%20safe%20from%20the%20enemy%20if%20he%20is%20victorious.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovind%E2%80%99s%20methodology%20is%20quite%20effective%3A%20he%20outlines%20the%20political%20events%20and%20developments%20of%20our%20times%20and%20elaborates%20on%20the%20positions%20of%20Hindutva%20leaders%20that%20forms%20the%20ideological%20base%20for%20these.%20Then%20he%20brings%20out%20the%20underlying%20political%20philosophy%2C%20explaining%20the%20position%20of%20Vivekananda%2C%20both%20through%20analysis%20and%20presentation%20of%20historical%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20279px)%2085vw%2C%20279px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12160655%2F71B4qoHMXmL._AC_UF350350_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22279%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12160655%2F71B4qoHMXmL._AC_UF350350_QL80_.jpg%20237w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12160655%2F71B4qoHMXmL._AC_UF350350_QL80_-203x300.jpg%20203w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672718%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22412%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGovind%20Krishnan%20V.%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EVivekananda%2C%20the%20Philosopher%20of%20Freedom%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EAleph%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovind%20identifies%20the%20first%20contradiction%20between%20Vivekananda%20and%20Hindutva%20outlook%20in%20that%20the%20latter%20blames%20outsiders%2C%20be%20that%20the%20rule%20by%20Muslim%20kings%20or%20that%20of%20the%20British%20empire%20(dubbed%20Christian%20by%20the%20Hindu%20right).%20Vivekananda%20held%20that%20the%20downfall%20was%20due%20to%20the%20dominant%20castes%20of%20India%3A%20%E2%80%9COur%20aristocratic%20ancestors%20went%20on%20treading%20the%20common%20masses%20of%20our%20country%20underfoot%2C%20till%20they%20became%20helpless%2C%20till%20under%20this%20torment%20the%20poor%2C%20poor%20people%20nearly%20forgot%20that%20they%20were%20human%20beings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20Hindus%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20Shivaganga%2C%20during%20a%20welcome%20meeting%20after%20the%20American%20journey%2C%20Vivekananda%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20neither%20Vedandists%2C%20most%20of%20us%20now%2C%20nor%20Pauranikas%2C%20nor%20Tantrikas%2C%20we%20are%20just%20%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20Touchists%E2%80%99.%20Our%20religion%20is%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20Our%20God%20is%20the%20Cooking-pot%20and%20our%20religion%20is%2C%20%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20touch%20me.%20I%20am%20holy%E2%80%99.%20If%20this%20goes%20on%20for%20another%20century%20every%20one%20of%20us%20will%20be%20in%20the%20lunatic%20asylum.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVivekananda%20held%20not%20Hindu%20religion%20but%20Hindu%20society%20guilty%20for%20caste%20discrimination%20and%20exploitation.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20religion%20on%20earth%20preaches%20the%20dignity%20of%20humanity%20in%20such%20a%20lofty%20strain%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20and%20no%20religion%20on%20earth%20treads%20upon%20the%20necks%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20low%20in%20such%20a%20fashion%20as%20Hinduism.%E2%80%9D%20While%20Hindutva%20tries%20to%20consolidate%20power%20through%20manufactured%20and%20perceived%20fears%20and%20insecurities%20about%20the%20outsider%20expressed%20through%20symbols%20of%20power%2C%20Vivekananda%20is%20looking%20inwards%2C%20at%20concrete%20social%20situations%20and%20historical%20realities%2C%20with%20enormous%20ethical%20courage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outsider-villain%20is%20furthered%20through%20%E2%80%9Cforeign%20religions%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20Sangh%20narrative%20and%20Vivekananda%20not%20only%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20share%20the%20Hindu%20supremacist%20position%20but%20he%20actively%20opposes%20the%20parochial%20view.%20One%20of%20the%20two%20books%2C%20points%20out%20Govind%2C%20Vivekananda%20carried%20in%20his%20travels%20is%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Imitation%20of%20Christ%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20book%20on%20Christian%20mysticism%2C%20authored%20by%20Thomas%20a%20Kempis%20%E2%80%93%20he%20also%20later%20translated%20this%20book%20to%20Bengali%20with%20the%20title%20%3Cem%3EIshanusarana%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20is%20also%20brought%20to%20our%20notice%20that%20%E2%80%9CIn%20America%2C%20many%20of%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20lectures%20were%20held%20in%20Unitarian%20churches%E2%80%9D.%20Constance%20Towne%E2%80%99s%20account%20of%20a%20church%20visit%20demonstrates%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20attitude%20best%3A%20%E2%80%9CHe%20went%20to%20mass%20with%20me%20at%20St.%20Leo%E2%80%99s%20Church%2C%20the%20little%20one%20on%20Twenty-eight%20Street%E2%80%A6There%20he%20knelt%20at%20the%20high%20noon%20at%20the%20canon%20of%20the%20Mass.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Remembering%209%2F11%20Speech%20of%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20That%20Warned%20Us%20of%20the%20Dangers%20Posed%20by%20Fanaticism%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fremembering-9-11-speech-of-swami-vivekananda-that-warned-us-of-the-dangers-posed-by-fanaticism%5C%22%3ERemembering%209%2F11%20Speech%20of%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20That%20Warned%20Us%20of%20the%20Dangers%20Posed%20by%20Fanaticism%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovind%20narrates%20instances%20where%20Vivekananda%20defended%20the%20egalitarian%20outlook%20and%20universal%20fellow-feeling%20that%20Islam%20preached%20when%20Western%20Christians%20and%20missionaries%20tried%20to%20dismiss%20Islam%20as%20crazy%20and%20archaic.%20His%20appreciation%20for%20Mughal%20architecture%20and%20aesthetic%20surely%20reads%20as%20an%20antidote%20to%20the%20Hindutva%20project%2C%20which%20understands%20history%20as%20gravedigging%20of%20the%20present.%20In%20Christine%20Greenfield%E2%80%99s%20words%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Moghuls%20seemed%20to%20have%20cast%20a%20spell%20over%20Swami%20Vivekananda%2F%20He%20depicted%20this%20period%20of%20Indian%20history%20with%20such%20dramatic%20intensity%2C%20that%20the%20idea%20often%20came%20to%20us%20that%20he%20was%20telling%20the%20story%20of%20his%20own%20past.%E2%80%9D%20Govind%20maps%20the%20Muslim%20presences%20in%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20journey%20including%20Muslims%20whose%20hospitality%20he%20accepted%2C%20quite%20contrary%20to%20the%20prevailing%20norms.%20His%20response%20when%20questioned%20on%20staying%20and%20eating%20at%20a%20Muslim%20household%20is%20revealing%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20afraid%20of%20God%2C%20for%20he%20sanctions%20it.%20I%20am%20not%20afraid%20of%20the%20scriptures%20for%20they%20allow%20it%3A%20but%20I%20am%20afraid%20of%20you%20people%20and%20your%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovind%20situates%20Vivekananda%20in%20two%20traditions%3A%20one%2C%20in%20the%20Indic%20spiritual%20tradition%20as%20a%20practical%20vedanist%2C%20with%20a%20key%20social%20sense%20on%20hunger%20and%20backward%20suffering.%20Second%2C%20in%20the%20Victorian%20period%20as%20a%20person%20who%20is%20trying%20to%20creating%20an%20enabling%20theoretical%20perspective%2C%20using%20British%20empiricism%20and%20German%20idealism%20with%20a%20Romantic%20aesthetic.%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20insistence%20on%20individual%20freedom%20(%E2%80%9CLet%20men%20have%20liberty.%20That%20is%20the%20only%20condition%20for%20growth%E2%80%9D)%2C%20Govind%20substantiates%2C%20goes%20completely%20against%20a%20supremacist%20ideology%20and%20organisational%20set%20up%20of%20Hindutva%20organisations%20that%20seek%20complete%20submission%20of%20the%20individual.%20Govind%20historicises%20Vivekananda%20enough%20for%20the%20modern%20reader%2C%20by%20providing%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwhy%E2%80%9D%20for%20a%20number%20of%20his%20positions%20that%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20jar!%20The%20intellectual%20honesty%20with%20which%20such%20instances%20have%20been%20identified%20and%20presented%20is%20noteworthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovind%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20at%20all%20engage%20with%20the%20academically%20powerful%20post-colonial%20school%20of%20thought%20and%20its%20readings%20of%20Vivekananda%2C%20even%20as%20an%20exploration%20of%20the%20absence%20%E2%80%93%20in%20that%20the%20book%20is%20courageously%20unfashionable.%20The%20situating%20of%20Vivekananda%20in%20medieval%20Indian%20traditions%20remains%20half-hearted.%20In%20his%20insightful%20and%20nuanced%20comparing%20and%20contrasting%20of%20Vivekananda%20and%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20author%20does%20point%20to%20the%20theoretical%20possibility%20of%20capturing%20the%20visions%20of%20justice%20and%20equality%20%E2%80%93%20an%20idea%20to%20be%20furthered%20using%20Gandhian%20ethics%20and%20praxis%20%E2%80%93%20a%20link%20the%20book%20curiously%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20develop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20reading%20this%20book%2C%20one%20gets%20the%20sense%20of%20an%20amazingly%20free%20personality%20%E2%80%93%20one%20who%20cherished%20and%20upheld%20his%20religion%20and%20culture%20but%20with%20confidence%2C%20resourcefulness%2C%20grace%2C%20rigour%20and%20even%20wit.%20Vivekananda%20comes%20across%20as%20both%20a%20critical%20insider%20and%20a%20powerful%20spokesperson%20of%20Hindu%20religious%20thought%20in%20Govind%E2%80%99s%20articulation.%20The%20dyanamicity%20of%20an%20evolving%2C%20concrete%20world%20and%20guidance%20received%20for%20it%20from%20the%20abstract%2C%20ethical%20principles%20pushes%20him%2C%20perhaps%2C%20towards%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20universal%20religion.%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20views%20on%20women%E2%80%99s%20freedom%20(%E2%80%9Cthe%20best%20thermometer%20to%20the%20progress%20of%20a%20nation%20is%20its%20treatment%20of%20women%E2%80%9D)%2C%20much%20advanced%20for%20his%20age%2C%20shows%20the%20possibilities%20of%20freedom%20and%20the%20need%20to%20universalise%20it.%20This%20engagement%20with%20a%20changing%20world%20also%20counters%20the%20revivalist%20impulse%20of%20the%20Hindu%20majoritarian%20scheme.%20Reading%20about%20this%20Vivekananda%20is%20a%20heartily%20enabling%20process%2C%20one%20that%20makes%20hope%20possible%20and%20not%20despair%20convincing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Vivekananda%20Dismissed%20Hindutva%20View%20That%20Blames%20Foreign%20Invasions%20for%20India's%20Civilisational%20Decline%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fvivekananda-dismissed-hindutva-view-that-blames-foreign-invasions-for-indias-civilisational-decline%5C%22%3EVivekananda%20Dismissed%20Hindutva%20View%20That%20Blames%20Foreign%20Invasions%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20Civilisational%20Decline%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20book%E2%80%99s%20achievement%20is%20that%20the%20concluding%20lines%20of%20the%201893%20Chicago%20address%20feels%20like%20an%20apt%20and%20adequate%20summary%20of%20what%20Vivekananda%20tries%20to%20do%20through%20his%20life%20and%20work%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20and%20I%20fervently%20believe%20that%20the%20bell%20that%20tolled%20this%20morning%20in%20honour%20of%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20different%20religions%20of%20the%20earth%2C%20in%20this%20parliament%20assembled%2C%20is%20a%20death-knell%20to%20all%20fanaticism%2C%20that%20is%20the%20dealth-knell%20to%20all%20persecution%20with%20the%20sword%20or%20the%20pen%2C%20and%20to%20all%20uncharitable%20feelings%20between%20brethren%20wending%20their%20way%20to%20the%20same%20goal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20to%20this%2C%20the%20historic%20salutation%20of%20the%20speech%2C%20it%20looks%2C%20would%20write%20itself%3A%20%E2%80%9CSisters%20and%20brothers%20of%20America.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EN.P.%20Ashley%20teaches%20English%20at%20St.%20Stephen%E2%80%99s%20College%2C%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694515539000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F07191646%2FSwami_Vivekananda_at_Parliament_of_Religions.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Freading-vivekananda-against-the-hindutva-grain%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22September%2011%2C%202023%20was%20the%20130th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Chicago%20speech%20of%20Swami%20Vivekananda.%20Govind%20Krishnan%20V.%E2%80%99s%202023%20book%2C%C2%A0Vivekananda%2C%20the%20Philosopher%20of%20Freedom%2C%20makes%20a%20persuasive%20case%20for%20how%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20icon%20is%20its%20arch%20nemesis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Five%20children%20who%20travelled%20to%20Pakistan%20with%20Sara%20Sharif's%20father%20taken%20into%20care%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694515500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F70x70%2Fskynews-sara-sharif-adam-parker_6252958.png%3F20230816165026%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsara-sharif-five-children-who-travelled-to-pakistan-with-their-father-taken-into-custody-12959696%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Five%20children%20who%20travelled%20to%20Pakistan%20with%20the%20father%20and%20stepmother%20of%2010-year-old%20Sara%20Sharif%20will%20be%20taken%20into%20care%2C%20a%20judge%20has%20ruled.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A97%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsara-sharif-five-children-who-travelled-to-pakistan-with-their-father-taken-into-custody-12959696%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fsara-sharif-five-children-who-travelled-to-pakistan-with-their-father-taken-into-custody-12959696%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fsara-sharif-five-children-who-travelled-to-pakistan-with-their-father-taken-into-custody-12959696%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Calvin%20Harris%20gets%20married%20in%20secret%20ceremony%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694515010000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103605037%2Cimgsize-39352.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fcalvin-harris-ties-the-knot-with-fiance-vick-hope-in-intimate-wedding-ceremony%2Farticleshow%2F103606330.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103606330.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ECalvin%20Harris%2C%20the%2039-year-old%20DJ%2C%20has%20married%20his%20fianc%C3%A9%20Vick%20Hope%20in%20a%20quiet%20ceremony%20in%20northeast%20England.%20The%20wedding%20took%20place%20at%20Hulne%20Priory%20in%20Alnwick%2C%20Northumberland%2C%20with%20close%20friends%20and%20family%20in%20attendance.%20The%20reception%20was%20held%20in%20a%20tent%20decorated%20with%20flowers.%20The%20couple%20exchanged%20moving%20vows%20and%20had%20a%20special%20performance%20by%20Nile%20Rodgers%20and%20his%20band%20Chic.%20Other%20guests%20included%20BBC%20DJs%20Scott%20Mills%2C%20Vernon%20Kay%2C%20and%20Jordan%20North.%20This%20news%20comes%20shortly%20after%20Chris%20Evans%20also%20tied%20the%20knot%20with%20Alba%20Baptista%20in%20a%20secret%20ceremony.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fcalvin-harris-ties-the-knot-with-fiance-vick-hope-in-intimate-wedding-ceremony%2Farticleshow%2F103606330.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explainer%3A%20Why%20the%20Maratha%20Quota%20Agitation%20Has%20Put%20Successive%20Maharashtra%20Governments%20in%20a%20Bind%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F24182632%2Fmaratha-kH1E-621x414%2540LiveMint.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20fortnight%20ago%2C%20a%20young%20Maratha%20activist%20in%20Antarwali%20Sarathi%20village%20in%20Jalna%20district%20in%20Maharashtra%20sat%20on%20an%20indefinite%20hunger%20strike%2C%20demanding%20reservation%20for%20his%20community%20in%20the%20state.%20Manoj%20Jarange-Patil%2C%20the%20Maratha%20agitator%2C%20mostly%20unknown%20until%20the%20last%20month%2C%20has%20now%20become%20a%20household%20name%2C%20with%20the%20agitation%20taking%20an%20aggressive%20turn%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20three-decade-old%20demand%2C%20now%20revived%20by%20Jarange-Patil%2C%20went%20out%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20control%20with%20sporadic%20%3Cem%3Ebandhs%3C%2Fem%3E%20being%20announced%20across%20many%20districts.%20In%20some%20places%2C%20the%20agitation%20turned%20violent%20with%20the%20police%20resorting%20to%20lathi-charge%20on%20the%20protesters%2C%20further%20worsening%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20both%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assembly%20elections%20in%20sight%2C%20the%20vexed%20problem%20of%20Maratha%20reservation%20demand%20is%20once%20again%20back%20to%20dominate%20the%20state%20politics.%20For%20the%20past%20two%20weeks%2C%20political%20leaders%20across%20parties%20have%20been%20making%20a%20beeline%20to%20meet%20Jarange-Patil%20and%20extend%20their%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJarange-Patil%2C%20who%20has%20been%20active%20in%20Maratha%20politics%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20says%20he%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Capolitical%20person%E2%80%9D%2C%20working%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20his%20community.%20At%20the%20start%20of%20his%20career%2C%20he%20was%20active%20with%20a%20Maratha%20organisation%20headed%20by%20Purushottam%20Khedekar.%20He%20later%20started%20his%20own%20organisation%2C%20%E2%80%98Shivba%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20primary%20demands%20of%20this%20agitation%20is%20the%20issuance%20of%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates%20for%20all%20members%20of%20the%20Maratha%20community.%20The%20Maharashtra%20government%2C%20on%20September%207%2C%20issued%20a%20resolution%20saying%20that%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates%20will%20be%20issued%20to%20all%20Marathas%20from%20the%20Marathwada%20region%20who%20possess%20the%20%E2%80%98Nizam-era%E2%80%99%20documents%20such%20as%20revenue%2C%20educational%20and%20other%20supporting%20records%2C%20and%20if%20%E2%80%9CKunbi%E2%80%9D%20is%20mentioned%20in%20their%20genealogy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20resolution%20is%20not%20acceptable%20to%20Jarange-Patil%20and%20his%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20his%20protest%2C%20Jarange-Patil%20has%20maintained%20that%20he%20will%20continue%20the%20agitation%20until%20his%20demands%20are%20fully%20met.%20But%20he%20is%20willing%20to%20have%20a%20dialogue%20with%20the%20government.%20The%20government%20had%20called%20for%20an%20%E2%80%9Call-party%E2%80%9D%20meeting%20where%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20the%20home%20department%20would%20withdraw%20all%20the%20cases%20against%20the%20protesters%20in%20the%20Jalna%20district%20where%20the%20police%20had%20resorted%20to%20lathicharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChief%20minister%20Shinde%2C%20addressing%20the%20media%20late%20Monday%20evening%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20requested%20him%20%5BJarange-Patil%5D%20to%20give%20time%20to%20the%20Justice%20Shinde%20committee%20to%20set%20up%20(a%20proposal%20on%20the%20viability%20of%20giving%20Kunbi%20certificates%20to%20Marathas).%20We%20have%20also%20agreed%20to%20include%20him%20or%20his%20representative%20in%20the%20committee.%20We%20have%20also%20agreed%20to%20suspend%20three%20officials%20responsible%20for%20the%20lathicharge%2C%20expressing%20apology%20over%20the%20lathicharge%20incident.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShinde%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%2C%20is%20a%20Maratha%20leader.%20His%20deputy%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20is%20also%20from%20the%20dominant%20Maratha%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20community%2C%20estimated%20(although%20never%20enumerated)%20to%20constitute%20over%2033%25%20of%20the%20state%20population%2C%20enjoys%20political%20dominance%20in%20the%20state.%20A%20land-owning%20community%2C%20Marathas%20hold%20control%20over%20most%20sugar%20cooperatives%20in%20the%20state.%20Many%20privately%20run%20educational%20institutions%20belong%20to%20the%20community%20leaders.%20Since%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20state%20in%201960%2C%2012%20out%20of%2020%20chief%20ministers%20belonged%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20privileges%2C%20the%20community%20leaders%20say%2C%20have%20been%20enjoyed%20only%20by%20a%20handful%20of%20families.%20The%20community%2C%20as%20claimed%20by%20the%20agitators%2C%20continues%20to%20be%20marginalised%20by%20and%20large%20and%20has%20therefore%20been%20demanding%20reservation%20as%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20has%20had%20a%20long%20tradition%20of%20anti-Brahmin%20movements%2C%20led%20by%20Maratha%20stalwarts%20like%20Keshavrao%20Jedhe%20and%20Dinkarrao%20Jawalkar.%20The%20community%20is%20known%20for%20its%20violent%20and%20dominant%20caste%20pride.%20In%20the%20Maratha-majority%20villages%2C%20the%20caste-atrocities%20inflicted%20by%20the%20Marathas%20on%20the%20Dalit%20community%20is%20very%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20demand%20for%20Maratha%20reservation%20is%20not%20new%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%2032%20years%20ago%2C%20Mathadi%20Labour%20Union%20leader%20Annasaheb%20Patil%20first%20began%20the%20Maratha%20reservation%20agitation.%20The%20demand%20has%20time%20and%20again%20come%20up%2C%20mostly%20around%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20just%20months%20before%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20then%20state%20chief%20minister%20Prithviraj%20Chavan%2C%20relying%20on%20the%20then%20Narayan%20Rane%20committee%20report%2C%20brought%20in%20an%20ordinance%20introducing%2016%25%20reservation%20for%20the%20community%2C%20particularly%20in%20government%20jobs%20and%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20taken%20forward%20by%20the%20Devendra%20Fadnavis-led%20government%20in%202014.%20The%20Bombay%20high%20court%2C%20however%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-maratha-reservation-pleas-maharashtra%5C%22%3Ebrought%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%2016%25%20reservation%20down%20to%2013%25%20in%20jobs%20and%2012%25%20in%20education.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20quashed%20the%20quota%20altogether%20for%20Marathas.%20%E2%80%9CReservation%20cannot%20cross%20the%2050%25%20limit%20in%20states%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmaratha-quota-case-sc-declares-reservation-over-50-as-unconstitutional%5C%22%3Ethe%20court%20opined.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20trying%20hard%20to%20defuse%20the%20situation%20that%20Jarange-Patil%E2%80%99s%20agitation%20has%20led%20in%20the%20state.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20state%20has%20offered%20only%20a%20partial%20solution.%20Allowing%20the%20Maratha%20community%20into%20the%20OBC%20fold%20would%20mean%20eating%20up%20into%20the%20already%20limited%20pool.%20Many%20OBC%20communities%2C%20especially%20the%20Kunbi%20community%2C%20are%20already%20up%20in%20arms%20and%20are%20pushing%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20outfits%20belonging%20to%20the%20Kunbi%2C%20Mali%20and%20Dhangar%20communities%20have%20initiated%20protests%20across%20the%20state%20against%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20integrate%20Marathas%20as%20Kunbis%20in%20the%20OBC%20quota.%20While%20the%20state%20government%20is%20busy%20initiating%20dialogues%20with%20Jarange-Patil%20and%20other%20Maratha%20leaders%2C%20the%20OBCs%20say%20the%20government%20has%20completely%20ignored%20them.%20The%20leaders%20had%20decided%20to%20stage%20an%20indefinite%20sit-in%20protest%20beginning%20Sunday%20(September%2010)%20until%20the%20government%20assures%20them%20that%20it%20will%20not%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20has%20long%20been%20divided%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20Maratha%20and%20Kunbis%20as%20one.%20A%20meeting%20of%20the%20larger%20OBC%20community%20was%20recently%20organised%20in%20Nagpur.%20The%20OBC%20Mahasangh%20president%2C%20Baban%20Taywade%2C%20who%20attended%20the%20meeting%2C%20appealed%20to%20the%20OBC%20community%20to%20en%20masse%20oppose%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Marathas%20are%20a%20separate%20community%20and%20cannot%20be%20incorporated%20as%20a%20sub-caste%20in%20the%20OBC.%20The%20Marathas%20have%20been%20demanding%20reservation%20and%20we%20are%20not%20opposed%20to%20it.%20But%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20simply%20be%20bunched%20along%20with%20us.%20If%20the%20government%20is%20doing%20this%20under%20pressure%2C%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20oppose%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Taywade%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694514601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F24182632%2Fmaratha-kH1E-621x414%2540LiveMint.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fexplainer-why-the-maratha-quota-agitation-has-put-successive-maharashtra-governments-in-a-bind%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20of%20the%20primary%20demands%20of%20this%20agitation%20is%20the%20issuance%20of%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates%20for%20all%20members%20of%20the%20Maratha%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%