Gujarat%20and%20Rajasthan%20to%20understand%20the%20problems%20faced%20by%20farmers%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20she%20established%20an%20NGO%20named%20the%20Green%20Energy%20Foundation%20to%20provide%20solutions%20to%20farmers.%20The%20foundation%20focuses%20on%20the%20revival%20of%20water%20sources%20and%20implementing%20smart%20farming%20techniques%2C%20while%20empowering%20women%20in%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20childhood%20that%20sowed%20the%20seeds%20of%20change%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201149px)%20100vw%2C%201149px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsharmila-oswal-min-1694441116.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221149%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sharmila%20has%20worked%20with%20farmers%20across%20five%20states%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsharmila-oswal-min-1694441116.jpg%201149w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsharmila-oswal-min-1694441116-300x123.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsharmila-oswal-min-1694441116-500x205.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsharmila-oswal-min-1694441116-768x314.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsharmila-oswal-min-1694441116-150x61.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329607%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22470%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESharmila%20has%20worked%20with%20farmers%20across%20five%20states.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20late%2070s%2C%20Sharmila%E2%80%99s%20father%20ran%20a%20flour%20mill%20in%20Poynad%2C%20a%20small%20agrarian%20village%20near%20Alibaug%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%2