father%20and%20later%20her%20husband%20prioritised%20her%20education.%20However%2C%20the%20difficulties%20faced%20by%20the%20farming%20community%20that%20she%20witnessed%20growing%20up%2C%20such%20as%20failing%20crops%20and%20increasing%20debts%2C%20deeply%20affected%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20through%20close%20quarters%20what%20a%20farmer%20and%20his%20family%20go%20through%20when%20their%20crop%20fails%2C%20or%20when%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20rain.%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20towards%20finding%20solutions%20for%20these%20problems%2C%20as%20the%20water%20crisis%20was%20only%20increasing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20challenges%20inspired%20her%20to%20get%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20environmental%20and%20agricultural%20law%20in%20England%20after%20getting%20married.%20She%20worked%20in%20the%20UK%20from%201997%20to%201999%20and%20later%20moved%20to%20Canada%2C%20where%20she%20practised%20until%202007.%20Afterwards%2C%20she%20returned%20to%20her%20homeland%20in%20response%20to%20the%20difficulties%20faced%20by%20Indian%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20farmers%20switch%20to%20sustainable%20methods%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsharmila-2-1694440857.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sharmila%20is%20a%20social%20entreprenuer%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsharmila-2-1694440857.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsharmila-2-1694440857-300x244.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsharmila-2-1694440857-500x406.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsharmila-2-1694440857