0technology%20to%20more%20regions%20for%20the%20same%20crops.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNiqo-robotics-6-1694183935.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNiqo-robotics-6-1694183935-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNiqo-robotics-6-1694183935-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNiqo-robotics-6-1694183935-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNiqo-robotics-6-1694183935-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329518%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJaisimha%20intends%20to%20scale%20the%20technology%20to%20more%20regions%20for%20the%20same%20crops.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20technology%20is%20designed%20to%20spray%20pesticides%20on%20crops%20like%20cotton%20and%20chillies%20rather%20than%20paddy%20fields.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20challenges%20the%20company%20faces%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20Jaisimha%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20farmers%20are%20willing%20to%20accept%20the%20technology%2C%20they%20believe%20that%20the%20more%20you%20spray%2C%20the%20higher%20yield%20you%20get.%20It%20is%20a%20little%20challenging%20to%20make%20them%20understand%20the%20importance%20of%20selective%20spraying.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20team%20has%20sprayed%20over%201%20lakh%20acres%20of%20farmland%20so%20far.%20Jaisimha%20intends%20to%20scale%20the%20technology%20to%20more%20regions%20for%20the%20same%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnowing%20that%20his%20technology%20is%20helping%20some%20of%20Indian%20agriculture%E2%80%99s%20most%20pressing%20issues%20like%20labour%20shortage%20and%20resource%20efficiency%2C%20this%20entire%20endeavour%20has%20been