arRahayyal%2C%20and%20Muhammad%20Ahmed%20al-Munawar%20were%20behind%20the%20act.%20Bhanot%20displayed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325596%2Fjournalist-pir-muhammed-munis-letter-to-gandhi-sparked-champaran-satyagraha-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremarkable%20courage%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20she%20saved%20the%20lives%20of%20more%20than%20350%20passengers%20on%20board.%20For%20her%20gallantry%2C%20she%20was%20posthumously%20awarded%20the%20Ashoka%20Chakra%20in%201987.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20such%20hero%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20aviation%20domain%20was%20Captain%20Durba%20Banerjee.%20As%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20woman%20pilot%2C%20it%20suffices%20to%20say%20she%20took%20India%20to%20the%20skies%20through%20her%20work.%20When%20she%20joined%20Indian%20Airlines%20in%201956%2C%20it%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20women%20across%20India%20to%20shatter%20glass%20ceilings%20and%20step%20into%20leadership%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20turned%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326955%2Frare-pics-of-milestones-and-historic-moments-of-india-music-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeaf%20ear%20to%20stereotypes%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20clouded%20her%20path%20as%20she%20persisted%20in%20her%20endeavours.%20Throughout%20her%20career%2C%20she%20accumulated%20an%20impressive%20flight%20time%20of%20over%209%2C000%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Neerja%20and%20Captain%20Banerjee%20made%20their%20mark%20in%20the%20skies%2C%20Mumbai-born%20Persis%20Khambatta%20made%20it%20in%20front%20of%20the%20camera.%20Her%20career%20was%20tinged%20with%20successes%2C%20the%20most%20popular%20one%20being%20her%20role%20of%20Lieutenant%20Ilia%20in%20Star%20Trek%3A%20The%20Motion%20Picture%20in%201979.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20daring%20Khambatta%20went%20bald%20for%20it.%20Through%20her%20work%2C%20she%20is%20credited%20with%2