ost%2C%20Kanika%20says%2C%20she%20uses%20paddy%20residue%2C%20and%20stems%20of%20water%20hyacinth%2C%20and%20mixes%20it%20along%20with%20cow%20dung%20to%20turn%20this%20organic%20debris%20into%20worm%20castings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20use%20these%20worm%20castings%20over%20chemical-laden%20urea%20to%20improve%20the%20fertility%20of%20the%20soil%20and%20thereby%20their%20crops.%20Vermicompost%20contains%20high%20amounts%20of%20nitrogen%2C%20potassium%2C%20phosphorus%2C%20calcium%2C%20and%20magnesium%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20year%2C%20Kanika%20was%20able%20to%20produce%20800%20kilos%20of%20vermicompost.%20Back%20then%2C%20she%20sold%20the%20compost%20for%20Rs%2010%20per%20kg%20and%20utilised%20all%20the%20earnings%20to%20expand%20the%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20I%20had%20two%20cows%20but%20later%20I%20bought%20four%20more%20cows%20to%20get%20more%20cow%20dung.%20I%20also%20source%20at%20least%2030%20truckloads%20of%20cow%20dung%20from%20farmers%20to%20boost%20production%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20set%20up%2010%20vermicompost%20beds%20each%20of%2010%C3%973%20feet%20in%20size.%20In%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20she%20has%20also%20set%20up%20a%2085%C3%9735%20feet%20vermicompost%20bed%20on%201.5%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3Eland%20of%20her%20family.%20Today%2C%20she%20is%20able%20to%20produce%20up%20to%2035%20tonnes%20of%20vermicompost%20in%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1693896930.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kanika%20sells%20the%20products%20to%20Assam's%20agriculture%20department%20and%20to%20at%20least%2025%20nurseries%20across%20Meghalaya%2C%20Assam%2C%20Arunachal%2C%20and%20Nagaland.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%